bri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Your contributions to&nbsp;South American Initiative&nbsp;make the expansion of this project a reality and increase the number of nutritious meals and supplies available to struggling orphanages.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">We at&nbsp;SAI&nbsp;want to thank each of our donors for their generosity in helping us improve the lives of orphans in&nbsp;Venezuela.</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/May2021/helporph2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/May2021/helporph3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/May2021/helporph4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/May2021/helporph5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>','blog_posts/May2021/qjm5h7R9utKoHb0pySUA.jpg','feeding-orphaned-and-vulnerable-children','Every moment we dedicate ourselves to the orphans in Venezuela, we at South American Initiative feel driven to continue spreading our cause to help more children throughout Venezuela. Every donation represents another opportunity for us to not only give food, but also smiles and hope.','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-05-26 18:20:01','2022-06-30 23:40:31','Alimentando a niños huérfanos en Venezuela.','2021-05-25 14:19:00',14,NULL),(6,7,2,'Help Improve Orphans Lives in Venezuela','Help Improve Orphans Lives in Venezuela','Thanks to your generous donations we are now expanding our care for Venezuelan orphans. In the past, we have supported four different orphanages. Now we are in a position to add two more orphanages where we will continue to provide food, medicine, and medical care for these abandoned children.','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">\n<div class=\"timestamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\">\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Lunchtime_at_Venezuelan_Orphanage_.57_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Lunchtime_at_Venezuelan_Orphanage_.57_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI supported orphan children enjoy lunchtime!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Lunchtime_at_Venezuelan_Orphanage_.57_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI supported orphan children enjoy lunchtime!</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>SAI Grows Help for Orphans by Supporting Two More Orphanages</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Thanks to your generous donations we are now expanding our care for Venezuelan orphans. In the past, we have supported four different orphanages. Now we are in a position to add two more orphanages where we will continue to provide food, medicine, and medical care for these abandoned children.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>SAI\'s New Medical Clinic Helps Children 4-Days-A-Week</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Our new medical clinic in Valencia is now exclusively seeing children four-days-a-week. Most of these children are from the orphanages we support. We have also recently started a program that features one of our medical doctors visiting an orphanage once a week to perform medical exams on all the children.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">This is a Godsend for these children as many of them have medical conditions that do not require hospitalization but need the care of a medical doctor to diagnose and prescribe medicines that can care&nbsp;for&nbsp;various medical conditions of the orphans.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">For example, in one of our new orphanages, many of the children were experiencing bouts of diarrhea caused by drinking contaminated water and eating rotten food. After their medical examinations, the doctor determined that they had bacterial parasites and worms feeding in their stomachs. These children were exposed to dirty drinking water and bad food before they came to the orphanage.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Antibiotics Solve Most Stomach Problems</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Since we provide clean drinking water and fresh food to the orphanages we support, bad water and rotten food are not problems. But worms and bacterial parasites do not go away by simply drinking purified water and eating clean food. It takes a 14-day regimen of antibiotics to rid these kids of their stomach issues.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Once they get these medications, everything changes. Now they can spend their time playing, having fun, and studying instead of hiding in the bathroom all day in case they have an accident.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Super Sick Kids Go To The Hospital</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Some of the children that visit our new clinic and those we see at the orphanages have severe conditions. These children are critically sick and need hospitalization. We send them to local hospitals along with an adult advocate to make sure they get the care they need. We also provide medicine and food for the children that are admitted to the hospitals.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>All Orphans Now Get Regular Medical Exams</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">To help prevent these dire situations we have established a protocol that all orphans get regular medical exams. In this&nbsp; way,&nbsp; we can be sure that the kids are healthy and those that&nbsp;need professional medical care receive the care they need in a timely manner.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Make Sure These Kids are Not Forgotten</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Prior to SAI&nbsp;offering full healthcare to each orphan, many of these kids were suffering from conditions that occur due to insufficient medical care. Our mission is to make sure these children are not forgotten and that when the politics and economy improve in Venezuela, they will be good candidates for adoption or in good health when their parents are&nbsp;&nbsp; reunited with their children.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Future Young Adults Best Hope for Venezuela</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">As time passes, many of these orphans will outgrow their orphan status and become prospering young adults who are tasked with rebuilding Venezuela.&nbsp;Caring for these children assures that as they mature, they realize how important it is to help others in their deepest time of need and to keep the spirit of hope alive.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Help Us Increase Orphanage Food Deliveries by 20%</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">As the orphanages continue to accept abandoned children, they need more food and medicine to provide for the additional kids. That\'s why&nbsp;our goal is&nbsp;to increase our biweekly food deliveries by 20%. Growing children need more food, more medicine, more educational materials, and of course, more love! Your donations make this possible.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">The orphans we support, our SAI staff and volunteers, are grateful for your commitment to helping and your generous giving. You are truly walking the walk and talking the talk of delivering desperately needed humanitarian aid to Venezuelan orphans. Thank you!&nbsp;</span></p>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Orphanage_Food_Delivery_is_Exciting_for_Everyone.58_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Orphanage_Food_Delivery_is_Exciting_for_Everyone.58_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI orphanage food delivery day excitement for all\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Orphanage_Food_Delivery_is_Exciting_for_Everyone.58_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI orphanage food delivery day excitement for all</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Venezuelan_Orphans_Gather_for_Group_Picture.62_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Venezuelan_Orphans_Gather_for_Group_Picture.62_Large.JPG\" alt=\"Venezuelan orphans gather for pre-lunch photo!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Venezuelan_Orphans_Gather_for_Group_Picture.62_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Venezuelan orphans gather for pre-lunch photo!</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Orphans_Get_New_Shoes.63._Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Orphans_Get_New_Shoes.63._Large.JPG\" alt=\"Orphans gather to show-off their brand new shoes!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Orphans_Get_New_Shoes.63._Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Orphans gather to show-off their brand new shoes!</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/changed_Doctor_Examines_Orphan_Teenager.65_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/changed_Doctor_Examines_Orphan_Teenager.65_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI clinic doctor examines teenager at orphanage\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/changed_Doctor_Examines_Orphan_Teenager.65_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI clinic doctor examines teenager at orphanage</div>\n</div>','blog_posts/May2021/11Rg9wLVFJCfvsBkOSpx.jpg','help-improve-orphans-lives-in-venezuela','Thanks to your generous donations we are now expanding our care for Venezuelan orphans. In the past, we have supported four different orphanages. Now we are in a position to add two more orphanages where we will continue to provide food, medicine, and medical care for these abandoned children.','PUBLISHED',1,'2021-05-26 18:32:10','2022-06-30 23:42:47','Ayúdanos a mejorar la vida de los niños huérfanos en Venezuela','2021-05-25 14:31:00',14,NULL),(9,7,5,'SAI Expands Medical Care for Kids!','SAI Expands Medical Care for Kids','SAI Expands Medical Care for Kids!','<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">SAI Expands Medical Care for Kids!</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><strong>By Steven Malca - President</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/June2021/doc5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" /></strong></p>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: left;\">future mothers can now get ultrasounds at SAI\'s Clinic</em></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">SAI\'s Children\'s Clinic is now open to expectant mothers, infants, seniors and teens. This is the kind of help that many children need to get through these difficult times in Venezuela.</span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: center; line-height: 18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Dear Donors,</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">We would like to thank you for your continued support</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">. The SAI Medical Clinic has treated more than 125 new patients in February. Our clinic is open and thriving with a constant new patients waiting to be seen by our personal doctors. Everyone is excited to see the doctor because most of the doctors in Venezuela have left the country in search of more stable economic countries.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">SAI is expanding its ongoing medical program by adding a new ultrasound machine to its facility</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">. This will allow our doctors to preview a pregnant woman\'s uterus to determine the health and gender of the new baby. It also gives our doctors a view of the intestinal activity surrounding the bladder and stomach.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 12pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">In the United States, it is common for women to have ultrasound exams where their new baby is seen months before it is born. In Venezuela, this is not so easy, due to its availability for the lack of financial resources for medical teams and health professionals.</span></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\"><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20190603_120131_Large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/xQ5gMCsp5m7sCwZT3aY7tkSvI4JpYKvFXOwDuet78iv0ujBzrl3axl0ii701zkYBwWh51UCs5fhRhHiktHa4ymGQZbBwIg4G1jkGtgSjcVVZt_7k2AyBA7-vMnknvVghaZX4vgeL\" alt=\"\" /></a>\n<p><em>Ultrasounds are important to determinate the baby\'s health</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/wgamgfyOYrCL28qvCcrtVFf-ILVAaO16VAronOwIeVCHNsl6hEMSQM2FJFgV97XID4RgDZbEwm2GjDS6n61qjasI2ZsSSyGTmz3KnuooMqQ50RLmIn77Urtrah_n98SPeWQaMjcS\"><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/wgamgfyOYrCL28qvCcrtVFf-ILVAaO16VAronOwIeVCHNsl6hEMSQM2FJFgV97XID4RgDZbEwm2GjDS6n61qjasI2ZsSSyGTmz3KnuooMqQ50RLmIn77Urtrah_n98SPeWQaMjcS\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"panel-body\"><em>Many children are seen by our doctors each week</em></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\"><a href=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/Zt_O8uZ4J7vB3B3-Zo1YbLvV04B436DWboXaAhd3uaeiYZKL6WCntlAGhE_4dJZwNlXSt8WOkybc22gEy2riBNTvw8v00IRbsCRu60JSj_yqu8L1XPd-NW09q0lZnGFjZVVwPCLI\"><img style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/Zt_O8uZ4J7vB3B3-Zo1YbLvV04B436DWboXaAhd3uaeiYZKL6WCntlAGhE_4dJZwNlXSt8WOkybc22gEy2riBNTvw8v00IRbsCRu60JSj_yqu8L1XPd-NW09q0lZnGFjZVVwPCLI\" alt=\"\" /> </a></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\"><img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/0BKVUC0_0WcBrOPAzMYdQsrvTtO8Lp7DMMVDEfLgDCr8jlNEhCLZFWmHdnsHyMzBif4yc78mBfp6hDuS26VAENlFlsrrtmbs8JxFFEqliRvDQ1KIXXHavDR9Nm7nSKAl9mO--inJ\" />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','blog_posts/June2021/5viV4l3UH0IvioxnsBnG.jpg','sai-expands-medical-care-for-kids','SAI Expands Medical Care for Kids!','PUBLISHED',1,'2021-06-07 20:49:33','2022-07-01 00:48:50','SAI amplía su atención médica para niños','2021-06-07 16:48:00',12,NULL),(10,3,5,'SAI Venezuelan Children\'s Clinic Expansion','','Thanks to your generous donations, our new children\'s clinic is providing medical assistance to 195 patients per month. With a little extra funding, the clinic has the capacity to grow and care for additional children.','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\">\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/c90783136bfc4195817fec57e036f68a_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/c90783136bfc4195817fec57e036f68a_Large.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/c90783136bfc4195817fec57e036f68a_Large.jpg\" /></a><address>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">SAI Children\'s Medical Clinic Now Open&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Dear SAI Donor,</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">We would like to wish you and your family a happy new year!</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Thanks to your generous donations, our new children\'s clinic is providing medical assistance to 195 patients per month. With a little extra funding, the clinic has the capacity to grow and care for additional children.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">That\'s the reason the new children\'s clinic is so important for Venezuela\'s local communities. Early intervention for medical conditions in a child\'s life provides for a healthy future for these children.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Since Venezuelan hospitals are are no longer able to care for their sick with limited resources and staff, the new SAI medical clinic for children is filling the gap to help keep children alive and healthy.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\"><strong>SAI also continues to provide our orphans with vital needs such as food, educational supplies, and medicines.</strong><br /><br />Our goal is to be supportive for all those in Venezuela who are in their deepest time of need. Our doctors&nbsp; provide medical care for&nbsp; every child&nbsp; that walks through our door.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">SAI wishes you and your family to be safe and healthy during&nbsp; the new year.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Sincerely,</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Steven Malca -</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">President of </span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">South American Initiative</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</address><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_20201204_151050_1_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_20201204_151050_1_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Infant Care is a top Priority at new SAI Clinic\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_20201204_151050_1_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Infant Care is a top Priority at new SAI Clinic</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/saingoMD1235_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/saingoMD1235_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI Medical Clinic specializes in family medicine\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/saingoMD1235_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI Medical Clinic specializes in family medicine</div>\n&nbsp;</div>','blog_posts/June2021/94EjkZAhffnjTyCiQUyu.jpg','sai-venezuelan-children-s-clinic-expansion','Thanks to your generous donations, our new children\'s clinic is providing medical assistance to 195 patients per month. With a little extra funding, the clinic has the capacity to grow and care for additional children.','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-06-08 20:15:32','2022-07-01 00:45:50',NULL,'2021-06-08 16:14:00',12,NULL),(11,7,5,'A New Era In Venezuela with COVID-19','A New Era In Venezuela with COVID-19','A New Era In Venezuela with COVID-19','<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px;\">A New Era In Venezuela with COVID-19</span></strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_C_copy_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_C_copy_Large.jpg\" alt=\"New Staff Members Open SAI\'s Medical Clinic.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_C_copy_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">New Staff Members Open SAI\'s Medical Clinic.</div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">If you think your life has changed in America and the UK since the COVID-19 pandemic, you should see what&rsquo;s happening in Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">As I am sure you know, SAI has a rich history of delivering nutritious meals to patients in local Venezuelan hospitals. We&rsquo;ve always been welcome, but due to the virus, all that has come to a full STOP.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">New Rules About COVID-19 in Venezeulan Hospitals</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">With the failing medical system being pushed to the breaking point, the government has decided not to allow any humanitarian aid to hospital patients. This new rule is enacted by the government to prevent the spread of Covid-19.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">&nbsp;Clinic Opening</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">As you may know from our previous reports, we&rsquo;ve converted the first floor of our SAI headquarters in Venezuela to a medical clinic.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">This medical clinic is providing primary medical care to children and orphans to include medical examinations, testing and medications. We are reallocating our resources from the hospitals to the clinic to help children in need of medical care. The clinic is fully operational with two medical doctors and one full time receptionist.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAINGO1223_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAINGO1223_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Doctor gives medical exam to young orphan boy.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAINGO1223_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Doctor gives medical exam to young orphan boy.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_20200904_153638_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_20200904_153638_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Medical team examines orphan girl\'s tonsils.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_20200904_153638_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Medical team examines orphan girl\'s tonsils.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_MD_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_MD_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI medical Doctor examines orphan girl\'s ears.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_MD_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI medical Doctor examines orphan girl\'s ears.</div>','blog_posts/June2021/hwEUPpNmInSrY1CwRWvq.jpg','a-new-era-in-venezuela-with-covid-19','A New Era In Venezuela with COVID-19','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-06-08 20:20:02','2022-07-01 00:40:26',NULL,'2021-06-08 16:19:00',12,NULL),(12,3,2,'SAI Is Delivering Food To Orphanages In Venezuela','SAI Is Delivering Food To Orphanages In Venezuela','SAI Is Delivering Food To Orphanages In Venezuela','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\">\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages1112_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages1112_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI Team Delivering Food to Orphanages\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages1112_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">SAI is&nbsp; supporting orphanages with over 9831&nbsp;</span>meals for the past three months. These meals consist of protein, vegetables and fruits, to keep children healthy. We also provide a wide range of ongoing supplies, including much-needed medicines, hygienic products, clothing, shoes, and educational supplies.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Medical Care in Orphanages</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">SAI is Providing medical check-ups and support for our orphans. Our medical team visits the orphanages every two weeks. Doctors from the clinic check the health of orphans in each orphanage. Doctors also provide medicine such as antibiotics and vitamins.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">New Program (Physical Training in Orphanages)</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Now, SAI is providing Physical fitness to orphans. These programs are helping children develop physical and mental fitness. This training will help children increase strength, power, speed, endurance, agility, and balance. The training activities are walking, hiking, jogging, running, climbing, specialized exercises and resistive band exercises.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Your generous donations make our work possible and contribute to mental and physical health, education, food, and medicine for these orphaned children. The SAI would like to thank you for providing a life-changing impact to Venezuelan\'s orphans.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages1112212_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages1112212_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI is Delivering Food To Orphanages In Venezuela.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages1112212_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI is Delivering Food To Orphanages In Venezuela.</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages11122_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages11122_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI Medical Assistant Examines An Orphan Girl.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngoOrphanages11122_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI Medical Assistant Examines An Orphan Girl.</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_Medical_211_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_Medical_211_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI Medical Assistant Examines An Orphan Boy.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_Medical_211_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI Medical Assistant Examines An Orphan Boy.</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Saingo122_Large.jpeg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Saingo122_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Orphans receiving physical fitness from trainer.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Saingo122_Large.jpeg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Orphans receiving physical fitness from trainer.</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/saingo12121_Large.jpeg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/saingo12121_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Orphans receiving physical fitness from trainer.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/saingo12121_Large.jpeg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Orphans receiving physical fitness from trainer.</div>\n</div>','blog_posts/June2021/47vjywclhS3JlsLMQ4ZF.jpg','sai-is-delivering-food-to-orphanages-in-venezuela','sai-is-delivering-food-to-orphanages-in-venezuela','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-06-09 22:52:15','2022-06-30 23:30:00','SAI está entregando alimentos a orfanatos en Venezuela','2021-06-08 18:51:00',14,NULL),(14,7,1,'SAI - A&G New Sanctuary Grand Opening!','SAI - A&G New Sanctuary Grand Opening!','SAI - A&G New Sanctuary Grand Opening!','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\">\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<p><img class=\"mcnImage\" src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/0a698a559b6c350199dfb20d5/images/e8705c10-e5bc-4305-99a5-81fa36342d74.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" align=\"center\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">SAI - A&amp;G New Sanctuary Grand Opening!</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">This is the grand opening of the new&nbsp;SAI Animal Sanctuary in Venezuela. This photo features our team of SAI staff who have been the frontline workers completing the construction of this new facility to care for abandoned dogs in Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Experts estimate that there are over 3 million abandoned dogs roaming the streets of Venezuela. Our new facility offers food, medical care, vaccinations and adoption services for the pets who\'ve been rescued from the streets. Our team\'s goal is to rescue the dogs, bring them back to top health.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">You&rsquo;re Making Good Things Happen!</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />Thanks for showing your love of animals by giving graciously so we can represent you and provide the love, food, medicine, and care they deserve. With your support, we are making good things happen in the animal community! Please continue to donate so we can rescue even more abandoned pets in Venezuela. Thank you!</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\"><strong>Generous donors make our campaign for </strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Helping Abandoned Pets</strong>&nbsp;<strong>possible. If you love animals like we do, you know how important it is to support these wonderful creatures so they can continue to live and survive this national crisis.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://mcusercontent.com/0a698a559b6c350199dfb20d5/images/2a84328a-653c-4d4c-82bc-cfb0c68822b4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" data-file-id=\"2057142\" />&nbsp;<em><span style=\"color: #282828; font-size: 13.5pt; letter-spacing: -0.45pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">This photo shows the new staff on their first day at the sanctuary. The Veterinarian is in the middle with his assistants on both sides. These are the individuals who will be working to fill the sanctuary of shelter dogs. They will be treated like family, so they are prepared to be adopted by a loving family.</span></em></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a class=\"mcnButton \" style=\"color: #ffffff;\" title=\"Donate Now\" href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/pets-venezuela/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">&nbsp;Now</a>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>','blog_posts/June2021/gAnX13GdFXedJa68C3yf.png','sai-aandg-new-sanctuary-grand-opening','sai-aandg-new-sanctuary-grand-opening','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-06-09 23:29:21','2022-06-29 03:02:40','SAI - Gran Inauguración del Nuevo Santuario A&G','2021-06-09 19:28:00',15,NULL),(15,7,1,'Venezuela: Saving Abandoned Pets Lives','Venezuela: Saving Abandoned Pets Lives','Venezuela: Saving Abandoned Pets Lives','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\">\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/Sai212123_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/Sai212123_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI Volunteers care for Abandoned\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/Sai212123_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>SAI Volunteers care for Abandoned</em></div>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: center;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">SAI Supports 11 Animal Shelters Caring for 257 Dogs &amp; 65 Cats</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">As of this&nbsp;time, SAI with the help of A&amp;G is providing food and medicine for 322 animals. We support 11 independent animal shelters throughout the state of Carabobo, Venezuela.&nbsp;</span><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Many of these domestic pets come to these shelters from families that can no longer afford to feed and take care of their animals. Others are brought to us as &ldquo;street rescues&rdquo; with no home, no food, and no one to care for them.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 1.5px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Pictures Featuring Rescued Dogs</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 1.5px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">These images are something you can be proud of as they show the gratitude of our team&nbsp;experience from your generous donations.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 1.5px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 1.5px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Guard Dog Protects</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> Watchman from Poisonous Snake</span> &lsquo;Blondie the Snake Killer</strong></span><strong>&rsquo;</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 1.5px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"04xlpa\" style=\"color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; line-height: 1.5px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Security guards make their rounds at a local university with a brave dog named Blondie.</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">One day while making the rounds, a poisonous snake coiled up to strike the guard. To his amazement, Blondie gave notice of the snake with loud barks and quick movements. Just as the snake leaped to bite the guard, Blondie stepped in front of the guard and was bitten on his ear.</span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Within minutes Blondie killed the snake. First aid was performed. Upon recovery, his left ear remained lifeless and floppy while his other ear was full and erect. </span></span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"jsgrdq\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">According to Professor Maria, Blondie is now a legend at the university and is beloved by the entire security team and the faculty of Economic Sciences.</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI1233145_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI1233145_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI Volunteers give recent rescue a bath!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI1233145_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI Volunteers give recent rescue a bath!</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/saingo22222_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/saingo22222_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Everyone loves to feed the dogs! It\'s the best!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/saingo22222_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Everyone loves to feed the dogs! It\'s the best!</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI12111_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI12111_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Staff &amp; Volunteers give medical care to rescues.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI12111_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Staff &amp; Volunteers give medical care to rescues.</div>\n</div>','blog_posts/June2021/eoHOgwJCfOLwQX8Cd4cT.jpg','venezuela-saving-abandoned-pets-lives','venezuela-saving-abandoned-pets-lives','PUBLISHED',1,'2021-06-09 23:49:20','2022-06-29 02:51:14','Venezuela: Salvemos la vida de mascotas abandonadas','2020-09-20 19:47:00',15,NULL),(16,7,1,'SAI Creates Safe Haven For Abandoned Dogs','SAI Creates Safe Haven For Abandoned Dogs','SAI Creates Safe Haven For Abandoned Dogs','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\">\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/changed_DSC00877__copia_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/changed_DSC00877__copia_Large.JPG\" alt=\"Rescued pets in \'Dog Paradise\' thanks to SAI\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/changed_DSC00877__copia_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Rescued pets in \'Dog Paradise\' thanks to SAI</em></div>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px; color: #444444;\">Silent Victims of Venezuela Crisis</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">Caracas, Venezuela -</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">&nbsp;When people can not afford to feed themselves and their children, the first major decision they are faced with is, &ldquo;How are we going to feed our dog?&rdquo; The answer to that question is easy: &ldquo;Our kids and family come first.&rdquo;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">How Pets are Abandoned</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">Rather than watch their pets starve, they choose to abandon them in the streets. They simply drive 5-10 km from home, and then open the car door, let the pet out, and then quickly drive away. This is the typical way dogs are abandoned in Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">South American Initiative &amp; GlobalGiving to the Rescue</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">The best humanitarian action for these abandoned stray pets is to rescue them from the streets, nurse them back to health, give them vaccinations, regular feedings, lots of love, and attention.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">SAI Abandoned Pet Protocol</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">After all that is achieved, the next best move for each dog is to be adopted by a vetted, loving, responsible family. Thanks to our generous donors, this is the exact protocol SAI follows when rescuing abandoned dogs in Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">SAI takes it one step further by&nbsp;spaying or neutering&nbsp;the dogs when they are healthy enough to handle the surgery. With over 3 million stray dogs roaming the streets of Venezuela, it is important that we spray or neuter all of the animals.<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">Besides food, these rescue animals are given rabies, distemper &amp; parvo vaccinations, as well as a deworming treatment, and&nbsp;a fast-acting oral&nbsp;flea treatment.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">At SAI we do all this for our rescued dogs. It gives each dog an opportunity to be adopted by a loving, caring family.<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">We Need Your Help to Continue to Rescue Abandoned Pets</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #444444;\">For the past few months we have provided food and medical supplies to the following:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; color: #000000; font-size: medium;\" type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #444444; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">SEPTEMBER: 162&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">abandoned pets have received care (<strong>6 of the dogs&nbsp;</strong>were adopted).</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #444444; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">OCTOBER:168&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">abandoned pets have received care</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" styl