d-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: center;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">Thank you to all donors of GlobalGiving and SAI for supporting our cause. The information is reflective of the GlobalGiving and SAI campaign Helping Abandoned Pets.</span></em></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"progressReport\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReport\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReport\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReport\"><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3313_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3313_Large.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3313_Large.JPG\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"progressReport\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReport\"><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3301_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3301_Large.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3301_Large.JPG\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_7536_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_7536_Large.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_7536_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>','blog_posts/June2021/leOYUePAswwfIfH6EM5j.jpg','because-they-also-matter','because-they-also-matter','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-06-10 00:55:40','2022-06-30 07:18:59','Porque ellos también importan','2021-06-09 20:55:00',15,NULL),(20,7,1,'Improving the Lives of Abandoned Pets','','Improving the Lives of Abandoned Pets','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\">\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_58_de_59_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_58_de_59_Large.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_58_de_59_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">The South American Initiative team</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;has a soft spot in our hearts for this cause. Sadly, many pets in&nbsp;<strong>Venezuela</strong>&nbsp;do not receive the treatment and/or care they need to survive. Our team decided to start this project to provide pets with the food, medicine, and other care products they need during these hard times.<br /><br />Each month, we have provided significant aid to allow our&nbsp;<strong>Venezuelan</strong>&nbsp;team to care for the&nbsp;<strong>abandoned and neglected pets</strong>&nbsp;in critical states of health.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45p