al; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"s1\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIzoo1211_Large.png\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIzoo1211_Large.png\" alt=\"SAI\'s team rescued this sloth and nurtured it back\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIzoo1211_Large.png\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">SAI\'s team rescued this sloth and nurtured it back</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIzoo1121_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIzoo1121_Large.jpg\" alt=\"An injured fox receiving medical treatment.\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIzoo1121_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">An injured fox receiving medical treatment.</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIZOO121_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIZOO121_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Adult Monkeys Eating Watermelon\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAIZOO121_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\">Adult Monkeys Eating Watermelon</div>\n</div>','blog_posts/June2021/cdRlJMkBAWrmTqWP35H2.jpg','sai-provides-food-medicine-and-love-to-zoo-animals','sai-provides-food-medicine-and-love-to-zoo-animals','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-06-10 01:57:49','2022-06-29 01:11:59','SAI proporciona alimentos, medicinas y amor a los animales del zoológico.','2021-06-05 21:57:00',17,NULL),(26,7,7,'Together we can make a huge difference','Together we can make a huge difference','Together we can make a huge difference','<div class=\"progressReport\">\n<div class=\"stamp\">\n<div class=\"timestamp\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/20190503_151949_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/20190503_151949_Large.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/20190503_151949_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<p><strong>Venezuela Neurosurgery: FINAL Project Update</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Valencia, Venezuela -</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> This report features summative details about the </span><strong>South American Initiative</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> project that provided Neurosurgery for drug-resistant epileptic children in Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p><strong>For Children Suffering Daily Epileptic Seizures</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In 2019 SAI launched a campaign to provide desperately need neurosurgery to children suffering from severe epileptic seizures every day.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The project included an implant device known as the </span><strong>Vagus Nerve Stimulator</strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that sends mild electrical stimulation to the brain when it detects the neurological symptoms of an impending epileptic seizure.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">SAI provided the surgical facility, paid for anesthesia, and the costs for the surgeons, nurses, and additional medical supplies.</span></p>\n<p><strong>Two Children Received Life-Changing Surgeries</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Two life-changing neurosurgeries were successfully performed. The first was for one young girl and the second for a young boy. These two children are now living normal lives without constant and unpredictable episodes of grand mal seizures - </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">also known as generalized</span><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tonic-clonic</span></em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> seizures</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Their parents expressed tremendous gratitude and joy that their children were selected for the surgery. Both families have written letters describing how their kid\'s lives have drastically changed for the better now that they can live without the constant fear of epileptic seizures. The little girl was having 7-10 seizures a day. Now she has none.</span></p>\n<p><strong>Families Amazed with Generosity of SAI<br /></strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Neither family could afford to pay for </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">the necessary tests just to see if their children were viable candidates for the neurosurgery. When they discovered their children had been approved for the surgery, they </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">were amazed at the generosity of SAI for providing such an expensive surgery at no cost to them. <br /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The 2019 project was made possible through generous support from SAI donors.</span></p>\n<p><strong>You Can Help Us Do Even More in 2020</strong></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you would like to know more about how SAI is helping desperate people in Venezuela, please take a look at the amazing projects SAI is leading to help orphan children, hospital patients, and abandoned animals in Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With your support, we can continue to save the lives of the most vulnerable and innocent during this time of political and economic crisis in Venezuela. Click on the link below to see more details about our general hospital campaign: </span><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/helping-hand-venezuela/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Let&rsquo;s Give A Helping Hand to Venezuela</strong></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/20190503_1623047_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/20190503_1623047_Large.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/20190503_1623047_Large.jpg\" /></a><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/SAINGO22123_Large.png\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/SAINGO22123_Large.png\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/SAINGO22123_Large.png\" /></a>&nbsp;</div>','blog_posts/June2021/o6EuLr0bw0dkplCsLclJ.jpg','together-we-can-make-a-huge-difference','together-we-can-make-a-huge-difference','PUBLISHED',0,'2021-06-10 02:11:49','2022-06-21 07:58:05','Juntos podemos hacer una gran diferencia','2021-06-09 22:11:00',20,NULL),(27,7,1,'SAI Venezuelan Medical Clinic Program','SAI Venezuelan Medical Clinic Program','SAI Venezuelan Medical Clinic Program','<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px;\">SAI Venezuelan Medical Clinic Program</span></strong></p>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/helping-hand-venezuela/reports/?subid=189554\">By steven malca - President</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_0973_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_0973_Large.JPG\" alt=\"Families receiving medical care and medicines\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_0973_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Families receiving medical care and medicines</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">SAI medical program has provided no cost medical care to over 400 children in the past three months in Venezuela. SAI is providing medical care to children from low income families who do not have the ability to afford medical care. In addition, SAI medical staff visits different orphanages each week providing medical care to the orphans. Children are receiving full medical examinations, vitamins to boost the immune system, and medications.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Magaly is a young pregnant woman with three kids. Each of the children received an examination from the pediatrician.&nbsp; Magaly was given a prenatal examination, ultrasound, pregnancy vitamins and supplements. Since January, over 50 expectant mothers received medical examinations, ultrasounds of their babies, vitamins and supplements to boost the health of the mother and child in the womb.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Our medical team and pediatrician partners have been supporting and improving the health and well-being of children, teenagers, families, and all communities. We are maintaining our biosecurity protocol to keep our patients and community safe. Most of our campaign has been focused&nbsp;on detecting chronic diseases at early ages. Due to low income and malnutrition of pregnant mothers, the high rate of neuropathology diseases in newborns has increased drastically in Venezuela. After our pediatrician evaluation, some children were referred for specialized examination that include laboratory testing, EKG, and kidney functions.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Thanks to your support, we are saving the lives of mothers\' and children. Your support has made an enormous impact for families and orphans in Venezuela.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_0973_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO12_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Patients waiting to be seen by doctors\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO12_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Patients waiting to be seen by doctors</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/IMG_0973_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseli