ects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=178830\">By steven malca - President</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAIAG_1212_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAIAG_1212_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI A&amp;G Dog playing!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAIAG_1212_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI A&amp;G Dog playing!</div>\n<p><strong style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Rescuing Dogs in Venezuela&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Dogs continue to be abandoned in Venezuela, and SAI A&amp;G&nbsp;continues to rescue them. All dogs need a home. The staff rescues stray dogs weekly. Many of the dogs we rescue come to us thin, dirty, and sick. We nurse the dogs back to health. We provide a loving caring environment for the dogs in the sanctuary.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">85% of dogs Need to be Neutered</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Most of the dogs we rescue need to be neutered. They are scheduled for surgery within a week of their arrival. As the dogs recover from the procedure, they are cared for and prepared for adoption. Recently, we neutered 15 dogs.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">New Water Station At SAI-A&amp;G Sanctuary</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Last week, we installed four new water stations at the sanctuary. These stations provide continual hydration for the dogs. These stations automatically refill the water supply. The stations are made from stainless steel to enhance sanitation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">We delivered Over 7,375 pounds of Dog Food from June to August</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">We support nine dog shelters with a total of 116 dogs and SAI A&amp;G sanctuary with over 70 dogs. Dog shelters desperately need equipment, food and medicines to care for the dogs. SAI donates food, medical supplies including medicine to dog shelters monthly.&nbsp;</span></p>\