.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG1212121_copy_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Puppies drinking from a water station.</div>','blog_posts/June2022/Rmo7ZxuYLZ6bgxRy3Q7n.jpg','rescuing-dogs-in-venezuela','Rescuing Dogs in Venezuela !','PUBLISHED',0,'2022-06-03 01:21:23','2022-06-29 03:22:40',NULL,'2021-10-17 21:20:00',15,NULL),(31,7,NULL,'Rescuing Stray Dogs: Dogs have A Second Chance!','Rescuing Stray Dogs: Dogs have A Second Chance!','Rescuing Stray Dogs: Dogs have A Second Chance!','<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=170061\">Rescuing Stray Dogs: Dogs have A Second Chance!</a></strong></span></h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=170061\">By Steven Malca - President</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_2218_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_2218_Large.JPG\" alt=\"New arrival shelter dogs greeted with love\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_2218_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">New arrival shelter dogs greeted with love</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">In Venezuela, many people who own dogs can\'t afford pet food because it\'s very expensive comparing to their salary. They have no other option besides abandoning their pets. This is where SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary saves the day by rescuing the dogs abandoned on the streets.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\"><br /><br /></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Medical Care: Spaying &amp; Neutering</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\"><br /><br /><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">When dogs come to the animal shelter they are examined by a veterinarian to determine the health of the dogs. Then, the vet places the dogs in one of these categories: healthy dogs, moderately injured dogs and severely&nbsp;injured dogs. The veterinarian provides the needed medical treatment that the dogs require.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">After a health examination, dogs get vaccinated. Then, they receive a warm bath, followed by a healthy meal. Dogs who need to be spayed are scheduled for surgery one week after their arrival.</span><br /><br /><strong><span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">SAI Deliver Dog Food to Dog Refuges &amp; Sanctuaries</span></strong><br /><br /><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">We delivered over 5,687 lbs of dog food from January to May.</span><br /><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">We provide support for 164 dogs at 9 different shelters. In the SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary, we provide safety, shelter, food, medical services, and spaying to over 45 dogs.</span><br /><br /><strong><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Thank you for being part of the SAI family!</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAingo121112_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAingo121112_Large.JPG\" alt=\"New Arrivals are receiving a bath and Spa Treat\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAingo121112_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0