ation-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/DSC02631_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/DSC02631_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI Volunteer provides joy to children in hospital\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/DSC02631_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI Volunteer provides joy to children in hospital</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828; letter-spacing: -0.45pt;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 30px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">GlobalGiving Project Update: Hospitals November 2019</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; line-height: 30px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">SAI Provided 8,225 meals for Hospital Patients in October!</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Thanks to&nbsp;our SAI and GlobalGiving&nbsp;donors, October was a breakthrough month for&nbsp;South American Initiative&rsquo;s&nbsp;project to help Venezuelan hospital patients. With our new kitchen facilities, we have increased our food production capabilities. SAI prepared and delivered a whopping 8,225 meals to patients in local public hospitals.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Upgraded Kitchens Expand Meal Distribution</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">During the past month, we have focused on providing more meals to individuals in&nbsp;Venezuelan&nbsp;public hospitals.<br /><br /></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Several days a week SAI staff and volunteers make and distribute fresh meals and desperately needed medicine. Our volunteers now make over a thousand arepas and other nutritious meals in our kitchens and then deliver them directly to patients in public hospitals.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">SAI Volunteers: Guardian Angels for the Sick</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Everyone is always excited to see our volunteers because they know we bring healthy food that may be their only nutritious meal of the day. When our volunteers arrive, patients say they are like guardian angels delivering food, medicine, and caring for those who cannot take care of themselves.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">We provide help where there is no help; compassion where there is no hope, food where there is no food, and medicine where there is no medicine.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Help Us Finish The Year Strong For the Holidays</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><