d-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #3e4b59; letter-spacing: 0.3pt; font-style: normal;\"><a style=\"color: blue;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/helping-hand-venezuela/reports/?subid=129109\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in; text-decoration-line: none;\">Human Kindness Overcomes Adversity</span></a></span></strong></h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/helping-hand-venezuela/reports/?subid=129109\">By Jimmy Pena - Project Leader</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/DSC09335_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/DSC09335_Large.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/DSC09335_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Living in Venezuela is More Difficult with Every Passing Day</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">The recent power cuts, shortage of water, gasoline, cash, and life-saving medicines have caused total chaos in the country.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">For most Venezuelans, these are the worst of times. There is one non-profit U.S. NGO that continues to provide support for those who simply cannot provide for themselves. This is the South American Initiative (SAI), with a team of staff and volunteers helping orphanages, hospitals, and animal shelters. These are the ones who need help the most.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Helping the Most Vulnerable</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">South American Initiative is committed to improving the lives of the most vulnerable people in Venezuela. For this reason, SAI has created a program called&nbsp;<em><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&ldquo;<span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Helping Venezuela Hospitals</span>&rdquo;</span></em>&nbsp;to make, prepare, and distribute healthy meals and medicine to patients and their families struggling from severe lack of food and money. Each meal is paid for by donors who have shown compassion in aiding people who are hospitalized in Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Food and Medical Supplies</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">SAI is distributing balanced, protein-rich meals and medical supplies to&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Give a Helping Hand to Venezuela</span></span></strong>. These meals are prepared under strict hospital regulations and are made specifically for the needs of each patient. In addition, much needed medical supplies are being distributed to improve patient care. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">5,839 Nutritious Meals</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 21.4667px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">In the past two months of April and May,&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">SAI</span></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Glo