ont-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">SAI continues to provide food, medicine, and medical care to orphans in Venezuela. SAI has implemented a physical training program that has significantly improved the lives of the orphans.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">The physical training is increasing their mental and cognitive abilities, physical reaction time and physical fitness. This program has also has helped the orphans with stress related to the pandemic lockdowns.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">SAI is providing fruits, vegetables, fish, chicken, eggs, pasta, arepa mix, rice, beans and more to the orphans.&nbsp; The orphans are receiving balanced nutritious meals. In addition, the orphans are receiving vitamin supplements.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vert