ine; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/fighting-malnutrion-venezuela/reports/?subid=127403\">By Jimmy Pena - Project Leader</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngo432_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngo432_Large.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAIngo432_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">When we think about the economic crisis in our country, we must focus our efforts on assisting the most vulnerable of people; orphans in&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Venezuela</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">. Orphanages do not receive the necessary funding to provide food for balanced sustained nutrition, for the orphans in their care. Malnutrition is the result due to the high cost of food.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">South American Initiative</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;is dedicated to aiding orphans in&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Venezuela</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">SAI</span><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-size: 14pt; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;is driven to expand our cause to help more orphanages throughout the country.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Thanks to all our faithful donors, the orphanages we are assisting are receiving continuous support from&nbsp;<span style=\"border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">SAI</span>. We provide daily food, clothing, shoes, and hygienic supp