font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/Diseo_sin_ttulo_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/Diseo_sin_ttulo_Large.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/40279/Diseo_sin_ttulo_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">After completing the first surgery successfully, it is time for our second patient, Andres.</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\"> He is a 17 year-old-boy living with his parents in the city of&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Caracas</span>. He frequently suffers epileptic seizures which affect every aspect of his life. It has made it impossible for him to enjoy a childhood like any other boy. Andres has difficulty performing physical activities such as swimming or running without worrying about having an epileptic seizure.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">SAI</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">&rsquo;s neurosurgery program is the only viable option for these children.</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\"> There are very few qualified doctors to carry out this procedure since many of these specialists have migrated to other countries. Not only are doctors scarce, but also the&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>VNS</strong></span>&nbsp;(<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>Vagus Nerve Stimulator</strong></span>) devices that are inserted into patients, are impossible for any Venezuelan to afford. The cost is about&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>$25,000</strong></span>&nbsp;just for the device, not including the surgery.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Thanks to the collaboration of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">LIVANOVA,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">we&rsquo;ve changed Andres\' life completely.</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\"> It has improved his confidence and his health in a surprising way. Now, his parents have something less to worry about: just being focused on his happiness.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">This beautiful family has extended its thanks to&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">LIVANOVA</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">,&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">SOUTH AMERICAN INITIATIVE,</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;and all the&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">DONORS&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">who have worked together to help Andres overcome the constant threat of seizures due to his drug-resistant epilepsy.</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">South American Initiative</span></strong></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">&nbsp;has always been concerned with the welfare of the neediest in Venezuela</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">. These surgeries represent a light in the midst of darkness for patients suffering from this life-threatening condition.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Many of these families believe there is no hope or help for their epileptic children due to the economic crisis in&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>Venezuela</strong></span>. At&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>SAI</strong></span>, our mission is to remind them there are kind and generous people who are putting their eyes on&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>Venezuela</strong></span>, willing to give a helping hand no matter how small or large their need.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.1pt; border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0in;\">Thank you to all donors of GlobalGiving, LIVANOVA, and SAI for supporting our cause. The information is reflective of the GlobalGiving and SAI campaign&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">&ldquo;Life-Saving Neurosurgery-Venezuela&rdquo;.</span></span></strong></em></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: non