ing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI medical team provides medical care, medications, and vitamins. Our medical team provides medical check-ups, and treatment that uncovers underlining conditions and provides preventative care.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI has added a new orphanage this month with over 180 orphans. This orphanage has the worst conditions that we have come across in years. These orphans need food, medical care, clothing, shoes, and school supplies. SAI is doing all we can with our limited resources. SAI needs your help to improve the quality of life of these orphans. Please contribute, every dollar counts for these orphans. Help us, help them!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">South America Initiative has been able to incorporate a personal trainer who visits several of the orphanages twice a week, providing physical fitness. The children have a complete exercise routine. Physical fitness provides a fundamental role in the orphans physical and mental health.</p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_122112_Large.jpg\"><img cla