rder-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=196091\">SAI-A&amp;G Sanctuary and Dog Shelter Update!</a></h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=196091\">By steven malca - Project leader</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary.12_jpg_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Dog rescue Venezuela\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/SAI_AG_Sanctuary.12_jpg_Large.jpg\" alt=\"New arrivals at SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary!\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary.12_jpg_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">New arrivals at SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary!</div>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">We are pleased to announce that the SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary is caring for between 90-100 dogs. Some of our dogs have been adopted by loving and caring families. Once Phase 2 is completed, the SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary will be able to care for over 170 dogs.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">A total of 17,710 lbs. of dog food has been distributed over the past 6 months to our sanctuary and 12 other dog shelters. 50.9% of the dog food purchased went to feeding the dogs at the SAI- A&amp;G sanctuary, and 49.1% of the dog food was distributed to our partner shelters.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">We are happy to be helping over 400+ dogs by providing food, veterinarian medical care, medicines, and vaccinations. The SAI Animal Rescue Program continues providing food for rescued dogs and providing vaccines to every new dog that arrives at our sanctuary. We have increased our help to partner shelters with staff and veterinary services.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">SAI A&amp;G welcomes our new veterinarian! With more than 20 years in the field, he has specialized training in pack behavior. He has expertise in Socialization Training for dogs and is sharing his expertise with the staff to improve socialization within the shelter!</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">We have added air conditioning and insulation to the surgery room to provide the dogs with an optimal environment during surgery and recovery. The air conditioning and insulation reduce the possibility of infection and provide a healthier environment.</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary21.12_jpg_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Save a dogs life.\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/SAI_AG_Sanctuary21.12_jpg_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Rescued dog receiving medical care!\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary21.12_jp