eline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI Provides Food To Orphans</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">South America Initiative continues providing food and medical care to orphanages in Venezuela. From July to October 2022, the SAI food distribution program has provided over 15,400 meals to 337 orphans in five different orphanages that receive our support!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI continues to provide ophans the following nutiritous food: rice, black beans, celery, green onion, fresh cilantro, chicken, sardines, potatoes, spaghetti, cornflour, tomatoes, carrots, wheat flour, and various fruit including papaya, bananas, strawberries, watermelons, pineapples, etc.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Many of the orphans are afflicted by illnesses due to prior inadequate medical care and nutrition, the priority of SAI is to provide comprehensive healthcare to every orphan! Our goal is to ensure that these orphans are healthy and happy!</p>\n<p><img title=\"Orphan boy receiving check up by doctor!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_32761.JPG\" alt=\"Orphan boy receiving check up by doctor!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: bo