rovides Food and Medical Care to Orphans in Venezuela!','PUBLISHED',0,'2023-01-23 22:26:05','2023-01-25 22:49:01',NULL,'2023-01-25 18:48:00',14,NULL),(64,9,NULL,'SAI Medical clinic provides vital medical care to children, seniors and pregnant!','SAI Medical clinic provides vital medical care to children, seniors and pregnant!','SAI Medical clinic provides vital medical care to children, seniors and pregnant!','<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/helping-hand-venezuela/reports/?subid=203637\">SAI Medical clinic provides vital medical care to children, seniors and pregnant!</a></h4>\n<p><img title=\"Patients thanking SAI doctors for medical care!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_24451.JPG\" alt=\"Patients thanking SAI doctors for medical care!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Patients thanking SAI doctors for medical care!</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI is providing free high-quality medical care for children, pregnant women, seniors, and orphans! SAI provides medications and healthcare services that are unattainable for many Venezuelans. Our medical staff provides primary and specialty care for patients.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">In the last three months, SAI has provided the following critical services: medical examinations, EKG assessment, gynecology, obstetrics, ultrasounds diagnostic services, newborn wellness check-ups, nutrition counseling, monthly wellness checkups for expecting mothers, medications, vitamins, and nutritional supplements at no cost to over 648 patients including seniors, pregnant women, children, newborns, and orphans as part of the SAI medical program.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI is working each day to save lives and create a brighter future!&nbsp; Be part of the change, join us by becoming a monthly donor! Venezuelan orphans, pregnant woman, children, and seniors need you! Help SAI make a difference.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><img title=\"Waiting to receive medical care by SAI doctors!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_13151.JPG\" alt=\"Waiting to receive medical care by SAI doctors!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family