5em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI-A&amp;G recently rescued a family of turtles and a baby African Hedgehog and relocated them to the zoo.&nbsp; SAI&rsquo;s primary goal is to protect and preserve all animal species in Venezuela!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">In Q3 2022, our team of volunteers and staff have distributed 2,685 lbs of food including bananas, eggs, plantain, papaya, sunflower, meat, oats, zucchini, beans, pumpkin, protein, mangos, watermelon, powdered milk, protein, carrots, corn peppers, wheat bran, tomato, and more.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">We are making a difference, thanks to your support, we will continue saving animal lives together!</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><img title=\"New arrival being cared for at the zoo!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_0955 (1).JPG\" alt=\"New arrival being cared for at the zoo!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans