"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">We have great news! We are delighted to announce that the SAI Medical Clinic has expanded its waiting room&nbsp;which has increased the capacity of patients that we can receive every day, letting us help more people. Our clinic is now larger and we are thrilled to help more people with their health needs. A television has been added to the newly renovated waiting room to provide entertainment to children. We thank you for your support in saving lives.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">We are glad to report that 716 patients, including children, pregnant women, elders, newborns, and orphans, received medical attention at SAI Medical Clinic during the course of the last three months. Our free services have included physical exams, EKG evaluations, diagnostic gynecological and obstetric ultrasound services, infant wellness checks, dietary advice, and monthly check-ups for expectant moms. Additionally, we have been able to provide our patients with free medications, vitamins, and nutritional supplements.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">At SAI, our passion and mission are to improve lives. We cordially welcome you to join us in creating genuine change by giving on a regular basis. We can work together to save lives and give those in need better futures with your support!&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Become a monthly donor and let&acute;s work toward a brighter future for in Venezuela. Thank you.</p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/2_Patients_waiting_in_our_new_waiting_room_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Medical Clinic SAI Venezuela \" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/October2023/2_Patients_waiting_in_our_new_waiting_room_Large1.jpeg\" alt=\"Patients waiting in our new waiting room - Venezuela Sai ngo\" width=\"720\" height=\"480\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/2_Patients_waiting_in_our_new_waiting_room_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Patients waiting in our new waiting room</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/3_Doctor_providing_medical_care_to_Venezuelan_child_Large.jpg\"><img clas