ic-2023-q2-update','SAI Medical Clinic 2023SAI Medical Clinic expands to serve more patients in Venezuela. In the last three months, we have provided free medical services to 716 people. Join as a monthly donor and help build a healthier future - your support saves lives! Q2 Update!','PUBLISHED',0,'2023-10-12 17:59:19','2023-10-12 18:30:10','Medical Clinic, SAI, health, Venezuela, health care, donation, free services','2023-08-06 13:56:00',12,NULL),(76,12,NULL,'SAI-A&G sanctuary 2023 Q2 Venezuela-Saving dogs','SAI-A&G sanctuary 2023 Q2 Venezuela-Saving dogs','Discover the impactful accomplishments of SAI\'s animal rescue program. In the second quarter, we distributed 7,370 lbs of dog food, benefiting our sanctuary and 18 partner shelters. Welcome Dr. Tariba, our new veterinarian, and explore improvements, such as a covered gazebo and benches for our beloved animals!','<div class=\"progressReportContainer progressReportStamp7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: url(\'https://www.globalgiving.org/img/projects/airmail_7.png\'); background-position: right top; background-repeat: no-repeat; min-height: 100px; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<div class=\"progressReport\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">\n<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=219427\">SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary 2023 Q2 Venezuela-Saving dogs</a></h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=219427\">By Jean Carlos - Project Leader</a></div>\n</div>\n<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230719_104644_975_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Veterinarian attending pets - SAI Venezuela\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/October2023/IMG_20230719_104644_975_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Welcome Dr. Tariba\" width=\"655\" height=\"491\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230719_104644_975_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888;\">Welcome Dr. Tariba</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\">In Q2 (April, May, June) SAI&rsquo;s animal rescue program distributed 3,575 Lbs (65 bags) of dog food for the dogs in the SAI-A&amp;G Sanctuary. 3,795 lbs (69 bags) of dog food were distributed among the 18 partner shelters that receive SAI-A&amp;G support. Total: 7,370 Lbs of dog food! (134 bags)</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\">We are thrilled to have Dr. Tariba, our new veterinarian join us at SAI! His extensive experience in veterinary medicine will be a great asset to our organization. He has implemented innovative approaches that help maintain the well-being of our animals while also making operations more efficient.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\">Also, we recently installed a covered rain gazebo in our front yard, providing our beloved pets with a sheltered space to relax and stay dry during rainy days. To add comfort, we placed dog benches.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">Thank you for your continued support, become a monthly donor and let&acute;s work toward a brighter future for all dogs in Venezuela.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230719_110647_691_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Chilling out on their new benches\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/October2023/IMG_20230719_110647_691_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Chilling out on their new benches\" width=\"655\" height=\"873\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230719_110647_691_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888;\">Chilling out on their new benches</div>\n<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230719_114350_531_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Dogs shelter SAI Venezuela-Relaxing\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/October2023/IMG_20230719_114350_531_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Relaxing\" width=\"655\" height=\"491\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230719_114350_531_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888;\">Relaxing</div>\n<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230727_103259_202_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Saved dogs from SAI Medical shelter Venezuela\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/October2023/IMG_20230727_103259_202_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Dogs enjoy playing in our backyard\" width=\"655\" height=\"873\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230727_103259_202_Large.jpg\" /></a>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888;\">Dogs enjoy playing in our backyard</div>\n</div>\n</div>','blog_posts/October2023/tZ67nnpV4eQm2th0tLCK.jpg','sai-aandg-sanctuary-2023-q2-venezuela-saving-dogs','Discover the impactful accomplishments of SAI\'s animal rescue program. In the second quarter, we distributed 7,370 lbs of dog food, benefiting our sanctuary and 18 partner shelters. Welcome Dr. Tariba, our new veterinarian, and explore improvements, such as a covered gazebo and benches for our beloved animals!','PUBLISHED',0,'2023-10-12 18:59:53','2023-10-23 23:41:50','Rescate Animal, Alimento para Perros, Veterinario, Refugios, Innovación en Medicina Veterinaria, SAI-A&G Sanctuary','2023-09-04 14:54:00',15,NULL),(77,12,NULL,'SAI providing food and medical care for orphans','SAI providing food and medical care for orphans - Vital Support: SAI Provides Food and Medical Care to Orphans in Venezuela','Discover how in the second quarter of 2023, SAI\'s Food Distribution Program provided 12,580 meals to 5 Venezuelan orphanages. In addition, our medical program ensures quality care for 291 orphans, offering free medical services, vitamins and medicines. Despite the challenges, we are determined to build a brighter future for these children. Join us as a monthly donor and make a difference.','<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 0.85em; font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 11pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><em>SAI providing food and medical care for orphans</em></span></span></strong></span></h4>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 11pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><em>By Jean Perez - Project Leader</em></span></span></span></strong></span></h4>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 11pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><em><img src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/October2023/3_Doctor_providing_medical_care_to_Venezuelan_child (1)1.jpg\" alt=\"SAI help orphans in Venezuela\" /></em></span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><em><br /></em></span></span></span></strong></span></h4>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 11pt; margin-bottom: 6pt; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><em>Orphans with our doctor</em></span></span></span></strong>