une2021\\/kziyPQiZnKEddlNjJEzG.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/F6HIBPFRpFB8t5mZ4gf9.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/duoKoRNJ7cPYZipfSMZo.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/ycWxUPwcKbTh5h16KTmN.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/dvtLQU7Jfndg3UgobG0M.jpg\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<h2><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">Summary</span></strong></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">The food crisis in Venezuela harms all components of society. No one seems to escape the reality which begins to leave permanent damages for future generations. 33% of children have a growth delay and this is a mental damage that will be with them throughout their lives. Malnutrition is taking lives in orphanages due to the lack of food supplies provided by the current government.</span></p>',NULL,'<script src=\"https://donorbox.org/widget.js\" paypalExpress=\"false\"></script><iframe src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/huerfanos-us?default_interval=o&hide_donation_meter=true\" name=\"donorbox\" allowpaymentrequest=\"allowpaymentrequest\" seamless=\"seamless\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" height=\"900px\" width=\"100%\" style=\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important\"></iframe>',NULL,'<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Resumen</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">La crisis alimentaria en Venezuela perjudica a todos los componentes de la sociedad. Nadie parece escapar de la realidad que comienza a dejar da&ntilde;os permanentes para las generaciones futuras. El 33% de los ni&ntilde;os tiene un retraso en el crecimiento y este es un da&ntilde;o mental que les acompa&ntilde;ar&aacute; durante toda su vida. La desnutrici&oacute;n est&aacute; cobrando vidas en los orfanatos debido a la falta de suministros de alimentos proporcionados por el gobierno actual.</span></p>'),(15,2,'Help Abandoned Venezuelan Pets','Help Abandoned Venezuelan Pets | Providing Food and Care','<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">Challenge</span></h3>\n<p><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">There are starving, diseased, injured, neglected dogs roaming the streets of Venezuela. Since many people in the country are unable to afford medical care and food for their dogs, people abandon their dogs and the dogs are forced to live on the<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>streets. The atrocity is caused by the severe collapse of Venezuela\'s economy, government services, and government infrastructure.</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">Solution</span></h3>\n<p><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">SAI-A&amp;G Sanctuary rescues and rehabilitates abandoned dogs at our facility. Dogs are cared for by our veterinarian and his team and brought back to health, neuteured/spayed, and given life-saving medication and vaccinations.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>Our facility has a surgery room, over 2 acres of outdoor space, dog cots, automated water fountains,&nbsp;<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and containment areas for sick rescues and aggressive dogs. We are a no-kill sanctuary. We also provide food and medical services to partner shelters</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\"><strong><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-size: 18pt;\">Long-Term Impact</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">SAI-A&amp;G Sanctuary will continue to rescue dogs and provide medical care, food, spaying/neutering,<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>and long-term care with hopeful adoptions. SAI-A&amp;G will expand the number of partner shelters that receive food, medical care and medicine and increase the number of states where we are able to assist.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\"><strong><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-size: 18pt;\">Donate To Help Venezuela Today</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">Make a tax deductible donation to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e9; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">help Venezuela</span></a>&nbsp;from our website.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e9; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">South American Initiative</span></a>&nbsp;are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization commited to providing relief to the most poverty stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help to provide necessary food, clothes, and more to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/orphans-venezuela/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e9; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">Venezuelan orphans</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e9; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">hospitals</span></a>, and more. Learn more about our organization when you visit our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e9; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">about us</span></a>&nbsp;page.</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">Related Articles</span></h3>\n<p><span class=\"s3\" style=\"font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">1.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2016/10/03/americas/venezuela-abandoned-pets-crisis/index.html\"><span class=\"s4\" style=\"font-kerning: none; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">Abandoned: The four-legged victims of Venezuela\'s economic crisis</span></a>&nbsp;- CNN<br />2.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/venezuela-s-abandoned-dogs-a7338011.html\"><span class=\"s4\" style=\"font-kerning: none; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">Venezuela&rsquo;s abandoned dogs: with runaway inflation, people can no longer afford their pets</span></a>&nbsp;- Independent<br />3.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/in-sight/wp/2016/09/26/heartbreaking-photos-show-venezuelas-abandoned-dogs/?utm_term=.4394ac4c0b90\"><span class=\"s4\" style=\"font-kerning: none; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e9;\">Heartbreaking photos show Venezuela&rsquo;s abandoned dogs</span></a>&nbsp;- The Washington Post</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','pages/May2021/TolpGPSVkhFytOIOUpHp.jpeg','pets-venezuela','Animals in Venezuela are suffering. SAI will help through alliances with other non-profit organizations to supply provisions for necessary care.','ACTIVE','2021-05-19 18:52:30','2022-11-03 19:19:17','campaign','[\"pages\\/May2021\\/byxd8cMMY8gNPsM7oLuI.jpeg\"]','<iframe class=\"ifrimi\" src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/pets-us?only_donation_meter=true&amp;donation_meter_color=%232ecc71\" width=\"100%\" style=\" max-height: 93px !important; height: 92px;\" seamless=\"seamless\" name=\"donorbox\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-donorbox-id=\"DonorBox-f1\"></iframe> <iframe class=\"aframa\" src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/pets-us?hide_donation_meter=true\" height=\"685px\" width=\"100%\" style=\"max-height: none !important; height: 1239px;\" seamless=\"seamless\" name=\"donorbox\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowpaymentrequest=\"\" data-donorbox-id=\"DonorBox-f2\"></iframe>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<h3 class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000; color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-size: 21pt; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">Summary</span></h3>\r\n<p><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif;\">There are tens of thousands of dogs roaming the streets of Venezuela! The dogs are starving, injured, sick, abused and neglected. Dog owners in Venezuela have been forced to abandon their pets because dog food and medical care has become unaffordable due to the economic crisis plaguing the country. We have come to the rescue! SAI-A&amp;G has built the largest no-kill sanctuary in Venezuela to rescue, rehabilitate, provide medical care, neutering/spaying and shelter to homeless dogs!</span></p>',NULL,'<script src=\"https://donorbox.org/widget.js\" paypalExpress=\"false\"></script><iframe src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/mascotas-us?default_interval=o&hide_donation_meter=true\" name=\"donorbox\" allowpaymentrequest=\"allowpaymentrequest\" seamless=\"seamless\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" height=\"900px\" width=\"100%\" style=\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important\"></iframe>',NULL,'<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Resumen</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">Hay miles de perros vagando en las calles de Venezuela. Perros hambrientos, enfermos, lastimados, abusados y abandonados. Los due&ntilde;os de perros de Venezuela han sido forzados a abandonar a sus mascotas porque la comida y medicinas se han vuelto inaccesibles monetariamente debido a la crisis econ&oacute;mica que invade la naci&oacute;n. Por ello hemos venido al rescate. SAI-A&amp;G ha construido el santuario m&aacute;s grande de perros en Venezuela para rescatar, brindar soporte m&eacute;dico y refugio a los perros sin hogar.</span></p>'),(16,2,'Help Venezuelan Refugees','Help Venezuela\'s Refugee Crisis %%page%% - 501(c)(3) Nonprofit Organization','<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\"><strong>Challenge</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\">Due to hyper-inflation caused by the failing government, many Venezuelans are fleeing the country. According to the Colombian government, one million Venezuelans have entered Columbia and 660,000 have remained. The WFP estimates that 90% of these refugees do not have enough food and medical supplies to survive.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: Times; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\"><strong>Solution</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #000000;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\">This fund is helping to provide life-saving relief efforts to Venezuelan refugees living in refugee camps. In addition, the fund is assisting the communities that are receiving the refugees and helping them through their migration. SAI is committed to providing food, medicine and job training to refugees in need.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margi