-webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e3;\">South American Initiative</span></a>&nbsp;are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization commited to providing relief to the most poverty stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help to provide necessary food, clothes, and more to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/orphans-venezuela/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e3; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e3;\">Venezuelan orphans</span></a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e3; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e3;\">hospitals</span></a>, and more. Learn more about our organization when you visit our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\"><span class=\"s2\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-kerning: none; color: #0000e3; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #0000e3;\">about us</span></a> page.</span></p>','pages/June2022/Exz8hR06VO6LdpZ5bfid.jpg','venezuelan-refugee-fund','Do your part to help during the Venezuela refugee crisis. Donate now with a tax deductible gift to help those most in need during this crisis.','ACTIVE','2021-05-19 20:58:17','2022-10-19 06:08:36','campaign',NULL,'<iframe class=\"ifrimi\" src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/venezuelan-refugee-fund?only_donation_meter=true&amp;donation_meter_color=%232ecc71\" width=\"100%\" style=\" max-height: 93px !important; height: 92px;\" seamless=\"seamless\" name=\"donorbox\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-donorbox-id=\"DonorBox-f1\"></iframe><iframe class=\"aframa\" src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/venezuelan-refugee-fund?hide_donation_meter=true\" height=\"685px\" width=\"100%\" style=\" max-height: none !important; height: 1167px;\" seamless=\"seamless\" name=\"donorbox\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowpaymentrequest=\"\" data-donorbox-id=\"DonorBox-f2\"></iframe>',NULL,NULL,'[\"pages\\/May2021\\/Lgq1YTsBvsbcwzzbMmi8.jpeg\",\"pages\\/May2021\\/fIKptAe1hfw2sOFiRVJE.jpeg\",\"pages\\/May2021\\/zvBjM5ydYROw3fmTLXNw.jpeg\",\"pages\\/May2021\\/KWvZ6UBipOrsiMfxjG4b.jpeg\",\"pages\\/May2021\\/V39LCqMJglN1TFwcWMZ2.jpeg\",\"pages\\/May2021\\/wVAjpxnZShUQNuPTAwA4.jpeg\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p class=\"p1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 24px; line-height: normal; font-family: Verdana; color: #343434; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #343434;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\"><strong>Summary</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #343434; -webkit-text-stroke-color: #343434;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"font-kerning: none;\">Entire families are forced to leave their homes with only what they can carry on their backs. The long journey across the Colombian border has become very common these days. The majority of Venezuelan refugees, who make it into Colombia, are sleeping in refugee camps, unemployed and without enough food. This fund will support Venezuelan refugees. We will work with other organizations in the Colombia&ndash;Venezuela border who are committed to providing assistance and support to those in need.</span></p>',NULL,'<script src=\"https://donorbox.org/widget.js\" paypalExpress=\"false\"></script><iframe src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/fondo-venezolanos-refugiados\" name=\"donorbox\" allowpaymentrequest=\"allowpaymentrequest\" seamless=\"seamless\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" height=\"900px\" width=\"100%\" style=\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height:none!important\"></iframe>',NULL,'<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Resumen</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">Familias enteras se ven obligadas a abandonar sus hogares con solo lo que pueden cargar a sus espaldas. El largo viaje a trav&eacute;s de la frontera con Colombia se ha vuelto muy com&uacute;n en estos d&iacute;as. La mayor&iacute;a de los refugiados venezolanos que llegan a Colombia duermen en campos de refugiados, est&aacute;n desempleados y no tienen suficiente comida. Este fondo apoyar&aacute; a los refugiados venezolanos. Trabajaremos con otras organizaciones en la frontera entre Colombia y Venezuela que se comprometan a brindar asistencia y apoyo a quienes lo necesiten.</span></p>'),(17,2,'Endangered Animal Rescue Fund - Zoo Animal Venezuelan - SAI','Endangered Animal Rescue Fund - Help Zoo Animal Venezuela - SAI','<h2>Challenge</h2>\n<p>Due to current government corruption, there have been difficulties with the animals getting the help they need. The private zoos suffer because of the economic crash and lessening of tourism as a result of the crisis. The public zoos suffer the worst because of the lack of funds and corruption from the current regime. The challenge is being able to identify the needs of private and public zoos and getting food and medical treatment.</p>\n<h2><strong>Solution</strong></h2>\n<p>South American Initiative will step in to fill this gap providing food and medical care to neglected animals that are suffering in these zoos. We are presently working with two zoos and one animal refuge in providing food and medical care to these animals, and plan to work with many more.</p>\n<h2><strong>Long-Term Impact</strong></h2>\n<p>South American Initiative&rsquo;s long-term goal is to feed sick and neglected animals, providing them with the proper care and nutrition in zoos throughout Venezuela. With your support, we will save these animals and be able to expand our resources throughout the country.</p>\n<h3>Donate To Help Venezuela Today</h3>\n<p>Make a tax deductible donation to <a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\">help Venezuela</a> from our website. <a href=\"https://sai.ngo/\">South American Initiative</a> are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization commited to providing relief to the most poverty stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help to provide necessary food, clothes, and more to <a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/orphans-venezuela/\">Venezuelan orphans</a>, <a href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\">hospitals</a>, and more. Learn more about our organization when you visit our <a href=\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\">about us</a> page.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','pages/May2021/8lkWrF8zk3ytXh3r85M9.jpg','endangered-animal-rescue-fund-venezuela-zoo','Help support endangered animals in zoos across Venezuela during this economic crisis. Your donation is tax deductible. Help Venezuela\'s animals today.','ACTIVE','2021-05-19 22:14:49','2022-10-24 23:40:48','campaign',NULL,'<iframe class=\"ifrimi\" src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/endangered-animal-rescue-fund?a=b\" height=\"685px\" width=\"100%\" style=\"max-height: none !important; height: 1085px;\" seamless=\"seamless\" name=\"donorbox\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-donorbox-id=\"DonorBox-f1\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\"></iframe>',NULL,NULL,'[\"pages\\/June2021\\/vG8ssKg01Dtj13CbVLQn.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/gjLzlWJtM3MaIBhG4J1P.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/Y8b6P0LpVJEnZ9QFuMBl.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/BObTaXfvb07fXxZqOIYe.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/p1USzne4Nji2Q9Xu1k1c.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/VyJCYIWU3TRHcSpybis7.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/POHoywPtCjayxxxDx7Dv.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/v24sS7eHvMvCN45IGhxj.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/7iH7UimZc4j9yIkci0bQ.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/dWj7RYIr0gKi4KnQzvzJ.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/wsRsaklDrqcHmuVGVTg5.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/tlqxk7GqBE8UGSilo0i8.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/qRvjUek33cUIUKWm5gy2.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/zWKGvwpMQnE7fmqGqMRd.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/Znem5m0fUfXGGsKYq9Y8.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/L55qoPMGzNzA2GprIH9Z.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/xk7yhX3hGrb65EifvV9D.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/Fi1QnTjglCXiowFD7Kl7.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/RWRJlI0bwzc9AfyUODmf.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/15THdLa0x1zVzYITETEn.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/jpk6RuiZhQ1bqIcUsjQw.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/kYHUg4WWcGNXaACPhuWx.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/BCDc07XKqKuLLeJZua5h.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/bWegVQDmo61zMg1h0oxT.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/IdbLsyBkQW1guDc15iHQ.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/hs7ArvUEzmcCBdEDEHY9.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/ZCNtxTNI9wucZhEhDx3s.jpg\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<h2><strong>Summary</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Due to the current political and economic situation plaguing Venezuela, large amounts of zoo animals are dying or are malnourished. Many of these zoos have had their animals become endangered due to starvation and lack of medical care. There is not enough money or resources to feed and care for animals in these zoos.</p>',NULL,'<iframe class=\"ifrimi\" src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/endangered-animal-rescue-fund?a=b\" height=\"685px\" width=\"100%\" style=\"max-height: none !important; height: 1085px;\" seamless=\"seamless\" name=\"donorbox\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" data-donorbox-id=\"DonorBox-f1\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\"></iframe>',NULL,'<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 42px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Resumen</strong></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">Debido a la actual situaci&oacute;n econ&oacute;mica y pol&iacute;tica que azota a Venezuela, grandes cantidades de animales del zool&oacute;gico est&aacute;n muriendo o est&aacute;n desnutridos. Muchos de estos zool&oacute;gicos han visto a sus animales en peligro de muerte debido al hambre y la falta de atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica. No hay suficiente dinero o recursos para alimentar y atender a los animales en estos zool&oacute;gicos.</span></p>'),(20,2,'Life-Saving Neurosurgery | Venezuela','The South American Initiative has the only medical program offering help to the epileptic children of Venezuela. SAI is supporting life-saving neurosurgery by providing Vagus Nerve Stimulator Implants (VNS) that offer relief from daily life-threatening seizures for kids suffering form epilepsy. Second only to the Red Cross, SAI\'s field team provides immediate help where it is needed most, to those who cannot take care of themselves -- sick children and orphans.','<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 36px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\">Donate To Help Venezuela Today</h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">Make a tax deductible donation to&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #db403e; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\" href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/help-venezuela/\">help Venezuela</a><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;from our website.&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #db403e; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\" href=\"https://sai.ngo/\">South American Initiative</a><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;are a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization commited to providing relief to the most poverty stricken people and areas of our beloved Venezuelan nation. Your secure online donation will help to provide necessary food, clothes, and more to&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #db403e; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\" href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/orphans-venezuela/\">Venezuelan orphans</a><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">,&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #db403e; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\" href=\"https://sai.ngo/project/hospitals/\">hospitals</a><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">, and more. Learn more about our organization when you visit our&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: #db403e; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\" href=\"https://sai.ngo/about-us/\">about us</a><span style=\"color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;page.</span></p>','pages/June2021/q5DAtGCGrl0PCVVxp1AI.jpg','south-american-initiative-vns',NULL,'ACTIVE','2021-06-07 17:19:46','2022-05-16 05:35:07','campaign',NULL,'<iframe src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/life-saving-neurosurgery-venezuela\" height=\"685px\" width=\"100%\" style=\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 310px; max-height: none !important; height: 959px;\" seamless=\"seamless\" name=\"donorbox\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowpaymentrequest=\"\" data-donorbox-id=\"DonorBox-f1\"></iframe>',NULL,NULL,'[\"pages\\/June2021\\/crr53ulrgO9NZNbUqOLZ.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/O9cOkBLP7ZYB75bHHsYr.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/GtDJudb7OSMkqI7b7RCj.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/lgcYWgQ3ocAq6Hg2GXiq.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/f4PtZsdraYXlIs3W8Vc2.jpg\",\"pages\\/June2021\\/P2sl6vZi1Loh7WjctxvV.jpg\"]','<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 36px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\">Challenge</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">As the political and economic crisis escalates in Venezuela, no one is taking care of sick, epileptic children and young adults. Epilepsy is a disorder of the central nervous system when brain activity becomes irregular, causing seizures or uncontrolled movements and behavior. Aggressive epilepsy result in 1-2 severe life-threatening seizures per day. With every seizure a small part of their brain dies and never recovers. Plus, many seizures cause head and limb injuries that could be fatal.</p>','<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 36px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\">Solution</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">The best procedure to halt seizures unresponsive to medication is called VNS (Vagus Nerve Stimulator) Therapy. A medical device is implanted in the patient\'s vagus nerve to provide a mild electrical pulse to the brain eliminating severe seizures. With a costs over $25,000, plus anesthesia, doctors &amp; nurses, these children nor their parents have the money to pay for the device and surgery, while others can\'t afford the necessary tests to see if they are viable candidates for the neurosurgery.</p>','<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 36px; color: #282828; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: justify;\">Long-Term Impact</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">These VNS Devices are donated by LIVA NOVA with 10 children benefiting from the surgery. Your donations pay for the surgical procedures, medications, and support. Venezuela\'s epileptic children desperately need your help to continue with the VNS Life-Saving Project at a cost of $250,000. With your help and a generous donation we can change the lives of Venezuelan children with severe epilepsy. The VNS Neurosurgery is the best second-chance at a good life these kids have.</p>','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">The South American Initiative has the only medical program offering help to the epileptic children of Venezuela. SAI is supporting life-saving neurosurgery by providing Vagus Nerve Stimulator Implants (VNS) that offer relief from daily life-threatening seizures for kids suffering form epilepsy. Second only to the Red Cross, SAI\'s field team provides immediate help where it is needed most, to those who cannot take care of themselves -- sick children and orphans.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(21,2,'Donate','Donate to help venezuela','<p style=\"text-ali