06-16 19:29:21'),(162,'blog_posts','body',34,'es','<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">Cl&iacute;nica M&eacute;dica Infantil SAI</span></strong></p>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/helping-hand-venezuela/reports/?subid=172943\">Por Steven Malca - Presidente</a></div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAIngo_Medical_Clinic112__Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAIngo_Medical_Clinic112__Large.jpg\" alt=\"Venezuelan girl receiving a medical checkup\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAIngo_Medical_Clinic112__Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Todos los ni&ntilde;os reciben atencion pediatrica en nuestra Clinica SAI</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">SAI ofrece servicios m&eacute;dicos a ni&ntilde;os y madres desfavorecidos</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">En Venezuela, no hay suficiente dinero para brindar atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica a los pobres. Los hospitales p&uacute;blicos tienen escasez de recursos para atender a las madres embarazadas y los ni&ntilde;os. Por eso, South American Initiative (SAI) est&aacute; ofreciendo atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica gratuita a los ni&ntilde;os, ya que muchos nunca han visto a un m&eacute;dico desde el d&iacute;a en que nacieron.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">Los ni&ntilde;os pueden ser vistos por un m&eacute;dico, obtener una receta para medicamentos de venta libre, sin cargo alguno. A las futuras madres se les ofrecen im&aacute;genes de ultrasonido gratuitas de su beb&eacute;. Estas im&aacute;genes crean alegr&iacute;a y emoci&oacute;n para los futuros padres.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">SAI ofrece nuevos programas m&eacute;dicos en la cl&iacute;nica</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">SAI ofrece un programa m&eacute;dico para futuras madres. Las mujeres embarazadas reciben un ultrasonido, un examen ginecol&oacute;gico y vitaminas prenatales durante su embarazo.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">Mujeres y ni&ntilde;os obtienen servicios m&eacute;dicos gratuitos</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">Durante los &uacute;ltimos dos meses, el personal m&eacute;dico de SAI brind&oacute; chequeos m&eacute;dicos gratuitos a 27 ni&ntilde;os, 45 hu&eacute;rfanos de orfanatos y 16 mujeres. Ademas nuestro programa, distribuy&oacute; 16 envases de f&oacute;rmulas para beb&eacute;s y vitaminas prenatales para mujeres embarazadas</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px;\">.</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">Gracias a sus generosas donaciones, podemos brindar servicios que cambian la vida de mujeres embarazadas y ni&ntilde;os.</span></em></strong></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_Childrens_Medical_Clinic_Large.