color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Aadir_un_poco_de_texto_1_Large.jpg\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Luchando contra la desnutrici&oacute;n en los orfanatos</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Aadir_un_poco_de_texto_1_Large.jpg\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Durante los &uacute;ltimos tres meses, SAI y donantes de GlobalGiving, han proporcionado lo siguiente:</span></strong></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Aadir_un_poco_de_texto_1_Large.jpg\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></a></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">MAYO:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\"> Se entregaron 5.264 comidas a los orfanatos.</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">JUNIO:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\"> Se entregaron 4.981 comidas a los orfanatos.</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">JULIO:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\"> Se entregaron 5.750 comidas a los orfanatos.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Aadir_un_poco_de_texto_1_Large.jpg\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">El n&uacute;mero total de comidas distribuidas fue: 15.995. Sus contribuciones a South American Initiative han incrementado la cantidad de comidas proporcionadas a los ni&ntilde;os hu&eacute;rfanos cuyos padres no pueden pagar para alimentarlos y albergarlos.</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Aadir_un_poco_de_texto_1_Large.jpg\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></a></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Los voluntarios y el personal de SAI brinda consuelo y atenci&oacute;n a estos ni&ntilde;os desfavorecidos, ense&ntilde;&aacute;ndoles el trabajo en equipo y un sentido de aprecio por los alimentos que reciben de nuestros generosos donantes de SAI y GlobalGiving.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/Aadir_un_poco_de_texto_1_Large.jpg\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></a></p>\n