itivos disponibles para los orfanatos en dificultades.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">En SAI queremos agradecer a cada uno de nuestros donantes por su generosidad por ayudarnos a mejorar las vidas de los ni&ntilde;os hu&eacute;rfanos en Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/May2021/helporph2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/May2021/helporph3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/storage/blog_posts/May2021/helporph4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #282828; font-family: \'Work Sans\'; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.6px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://sai.malcacorp.com/public/sto