</strong></p>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/fighting-malnutrion-venezuela/reports/?subid=178858\">Por Steven Malca - Presidente</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans3322_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans3322_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI Physical Training Program\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans3322_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">SAI contin&uacute;a brindando alimentos, medicinas y atenci&oacute;n m&eacute;dica a los ni&ntilde;os de Orfanatos &nbsp;en Venezuela. SAI ha implementado un programa de entrenamiento f&iacute;sico que ha mejorado significativamente la vida de los ni&ntilde;os. El entrenamiento f&iacute;sico est&aacute; aumentando sus capacidades mentales y cognitivas, el tiempo de reacci&oacute;n f&iacute;sica y la forma f&iacute;sica. Este programa tambi&eacute;n ha ayudado a los hu&eacute;rfanos con el estr&eacute;s relacionado con los confinamientos por la pandemia.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">SAI est&aacute; proporcionando frutas, verduras, pescado, pollo, huevos, pasta, harina para arepas, arroz, frijoles y mucho m&aacute;s. Todos nuestros orfanatos est&aacute;n recibiendo comidas nutritivas y balanceadas. Adem&aacute;s, de suplementos vitam&iacute;nicos y medicinas.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">En los &uacute;ltimos tres meses, con la generosa ayuda de los donantes de <strong>GlobalGiving</strong>, y <strong>SA</strong>I, se ha proporcionado: <strong>8,972 comidas a los orfanatos.</strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">Adicionalmente, los m&eacute;dicos de SAI realizan chequeos 2 veces al mes para los ni&ntilde;os. Estos chequeos pueden detectar cualquier problema m&eacute;dico subyacente y proporcionar tratamiento para las condiciones m&eacute;dicas que surjan. Adem&aacute;s, SAI proporciona a los hu&eacute;rfanos suministros higi&eacute;nicos.</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans332221_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans332221_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI Physical Training Program\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans332221_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Programa de entrenamiento fisico de SAI</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans33221_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans33221_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI medical doctor giving check up do you orphan\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_ngo_orphans33221_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Nuestros doctores en las visitas a los Orfanatos</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_Food_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_Food_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI Food Delivery\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_Food_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Programa de Alimentacion de SAI</div>','2022-06-16 01:11:10','2022-06-16 01:11:10'),(263,'blog_posts','excerpt',46,'es','¡Cambiando la vida de niños huérfanos en Venezuela!','2022-06-16 01:11:10','2022-06-16 01:11:10'),(264,'blog_posts','slug',46,'es'