teven Malca - Presidente</strong></div>\n<div class=\"byline\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3113_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3113_Large.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_3113_Large.JPG\" /></a>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 14pt 0in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; line-height: 32px; color: #282828;\">Porque ellos tambi&eacute;n importan</span></strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 14pt 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828;\">El equipo de South American Initiative, tiene una gran debilidad por los animales abandonados en&nbsp; Venezuela. Lamentablemente, muchas mascotas en Venezuela son abandonadas o descuidadas debido a la pobreza y la hambruna. No reciben el tratamiento y la atenci&oacute;n que necesitan para sobrevivir. Nuestro equipo decidi&oacute; poner en marcha este proyecto para proporcionar a estas mascotas alimentos, medicinas y otros productos de cuidado que necesitan durante estos tiempos dif&iacute;ciles.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 14pt 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828;\">Cada mes brindamos una importante ayuda a nuestro equipo en Venezuela para el cuidado de las mascotas abandonadas y desatendidas en estado cr&iacute;tico de salud.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 14pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px; color: #282828;\">Durante los &uacute;ltimos meses hemos proporcionado alimentos y suministros m&eacute;dicos:</span></strong></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; color: #000000; font-size: medium; margin-top: 0in;\" type=\"disc\">\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 14pt 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">OCTUBRE:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\"> 72 mascotas abandonadas han recibido atenci&oacute;n.</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">NOVIEMBRE:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\"> 98 mascotas abandonadas han recibido atenci&oacute;n.</span></li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 14pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #282828; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\">DICIEMBRE:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 28px;\"> 97 mascotas abandonadas han recibido atenci&oacute;n.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 14pt 0.5in; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: #000000; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; backgr