 0.025em;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/fighting-malnutrion-venezuela/reports/?subid=161945\">SAI Orphan Update: Venezuela!</a></span></h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/fighting-malnutrion-venezuela/reports/?subid=161945\">By Steven Malca - President</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI1232jpeg_Large.jpeg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI1232jpeg_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"The Joys of Christmas in Venezuela!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI1232jpeg_Large.jpeg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">The Joys of Christmas in Venezuela!</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Dear SAI Donors,</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">We would like to wish you and your family a Happy New Year!</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">SAI has provided desperately needed shoes to our orphans for Christmas. Each orphan received a brand new pair of shoes from Santa Claus. You should have seen the smiles and excitement on their faces when they recieved their new shoes.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Regular and consistent food deliveris keep the orphans well fed.&nbsp; We strive to provide nutritious food every day. SAI has provided 11,581&nbsp;meals for the past three months. These meals consist of protein, vegetables, and fruit, to keep our orphans healthy during their time of growth and development.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">We also provide medical check-ups and support for our orphans. The SAI doctors from the clinic go to each one of our orphanages to provide medical care and assistance.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">This is a Godsend for the the orphans to have a medical doctor to make house-calls to the orphanages.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Your generous donations make our work possible and contribute to the good health, education, and well being for these underprivileged children. </span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\">Thank you for making such a huge difference in the future of Venezuelan orphans.</span></strong><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/22_Large.jpeg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/22_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Young Orphan Girl Gets Medical Exam fro SAI Doctor\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/22_Large.jpeg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Young Orphan Girl Gets Medical Exam fro SAI Doctor</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAingo123_Large.jpeg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAingo123_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"SAI medical assistant examines orphan boy\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAingo123_Large.jpeg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI medical assistant examines orphan boy</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-ali