in: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/helping-hand-venezuela/reports/?subid=196293\">Por Steven Malca - Presidente.</a></h4>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO_Help_Venezuela_Medical_Clinic_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO_Help_Venezuela_Medical_Clinic_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Patients receiving medical care in our clinic!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO_Help_Venezuela_Medical_Clinic_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Pacientes recibiendo cuidado m&eacute;dico en nuestra cl&iacute;nica.</div>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ES\" style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">La cl&iacute;nica SAI se enorgullece en anunciar que ha expandido su programa m&eacute;dico en pro de proveer servicios m&eacute;dicos gratuitos de alta calidad para ni&ntilde;os, hu&eacute;rfanos y mujeres embarazadas. SAI facilita el alcance de medicinas y servicios m&eacute;dicos que son inaccesibles para muchos venezolanos. Nuestro equipo m&eacute;dico formado por profesionales en el campo, provee tratamiento de calidad a nuestros pacientes. SAI posee un equipo m&eacute;dico que trabaja a tiempo completo y le da la bienvenida a nuestra nueva pediatra con m&aacute;s de 10 a&ntilde;os de experiencia en el campo.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ES\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">En los &uacute;ltimos tres meses SAI ha proporcionado servicio m&eacute;dico a m&aacute;s de 830 pacientes. Continuamos trabajando para proveer servicio pedi&aacute;trico, ex&aacute;menes f&iacute;sicos, control pre-natal, ecograf&iacute;as, ginecolog&iacute;a, obstetricia, y suplementos nutricionales sin costo alguno.</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"ES\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Necesitamos tu ayuda para continuar ayudando y aumentar el alcance de nuestros servicios y medicinas. Estamos haciendo una diferencia en la vida de los ni&ntilde;os, ni&ntilde;as y mujeres embarazadas. Puedes convertirte en un donador mensual y ayudarnos a salvar vidas.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_childrens_medical_clinic_Venezuela12aw_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_childrens_medical_clinic_Venezuela12aw_Large.JPG\" alt=\"Patients waiting to be seen by medical staff!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_childrens_medical_clinic_Venezuela12aw_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Pacientes esperando para ser atendidos.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO_Large.JPG\" alt=\"Infant receiving a medical exam!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAI_NGO_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padd