eceiving vitamins to boost Immune system\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/29831/SAINGO_medical_clinicww_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Ni&ntilde;os recibiendo vitaminas que mejorar&aacute;n su sistema inmunol&oacute;gico.&nbsp;</div>','2022-08-05 20:01:42','2022-10-24 21:53:32'),(446,'blog_posts','excerpt',58,'es','SAI\'s Medical Clinic in Venezuela Update!','2022-08-05 20:01:42','2022-08-05 20:01:42'),(447,'blog_posts','slug',58,'es','clinica-medica-sai-en-venezuela','2022-08-05 20:01:42','2022-10-24 21:55:18'),(448,'blog_posts','meta_description',58,'es','Clinica de SAI en Venezuela','2022-08-05 20:01:42','2022-10-24 21:53:32'),(449,'blog_posts','title',59,'es','SAI está salvando huérfanos en Venezuela.','2022-08-05 20:17:04','2022-10-24 22:23:33'),(450,'blog_posts','seo_title',59,'es','SAI está salvando huérfanos en Venezuela.','2022-08-05 20:17:04','2022-10-24 22:23:33'),(451,'blog_posts','body',59,'es','<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/fighting-malnutrion-venezuela/reports/?subid=196089\">SAI est&aacute; salvando hu&eacute;rfanos en Venezuela.</a></h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/fighting-malnutrion-venezuela/reports/?subid=196089\">Por Steven Malca - Presidente.</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_1211_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Help Orphans Venezuela\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_1211_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Ophans giving a thumbs for the food!\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_1211_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Hu&eacute;rfanos felices con la ayuda de SAI.</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">La Iniciativa Suramericana (SAI) contin&uacute;a brindando ayuda a orfanatos en Venezuela. Durante los &uacute;ltimos tres meses, el programa de alimentaci&oacute;n ha distribuido m&aacute;s de 15.800 platos de comida que incluyen, prote&iacute;nas, vegetales, frutas, y arroz a los hu&eacute;rfanos. La mayor&iacute;a de estos ni&ntilde;os sufr&iacute;an de problemas de malnutrici&oacute;n. SAI est&aacute; entregando comidas nutritivas a los hu&eacute;rfanos.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">El equipo m&eacute;dico de SAI se encarga de proveer cuidado m&eacute;dico, medicinas y vitaminas, adem&aacute;s de los chequeos mensuales y tratamientos necesarios para el cuidado de la salud de los ni&ntilde;os en lo orfanatos.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Recientemente SAI ha agregado un nuevo orfanato a nuestro programa, con m&aacute;s de 180 huerfanos en &eacute;l. Este orfanato posee muy pocos recursos y es de los que en peores condiciones nos hemos encontrado desde hace a&ntilde;os. Estos ni&ntilde;os necesitan comida, medicinas, ropa, zapatos y &uacute;tiles escolares. En SAI estamos haciendo todo lo que podemos con nuestros limitados recursos. SAI necesita tu ayuda para mejorar la calidad de vida de estos hu&eacute;rfanos. Por favor contribuye con nosotros, cada d&oacute;lar cuenta para estos ni&ntilde;os. Ay&uacute;danos, Ay&uacute;dalos.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">La Iniciativa Suramericana ha incorporado un entrenador personal a nuestro programa que visitas varios orfanatos dos veces a la semana, brindando programas de entrenamiento f&iacute;sico. Los ni&ntilde;os tienen una rituna completa de ejercicios. El ejercicio f&iacute;sico tiene un papel importante en la salud mental y f&iacute;sica de los hu&eacute;rfanos.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_122112_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_122112_Large.jpg\" alt=\"These orphans desperately need your help!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_122112_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Estos hu&eacute;rfanos necesitan tu ayuda!</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAINGOops_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Help orphans\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/SAINGOops_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"SAI Doctors provide continual medical care!\" width=\"1024\" height=\"910\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAINGOops_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Los doctores de SAI brindan servicios m&eacute;dicos.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #f08b1d; font-weight: bold; outline: 0px; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_1232_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Help orphans\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_1232_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"SAI provides physical fitness!\" width=\"1024\" height=\"646\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/31552/SAI_NGO_Orphan_Venezuela_1232_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI brinda entrenamiento f&iacute;sico.</div>','2022-08-05 20:17:04','2022-10-24 22:23:33'),(452,'blog_posts','excerpt',59,'es','SAI is saving orphan\'s lives in Venezuela','2022-08-05 20:17:04','2022-08-05 20:17:04'),(453,'blog_posts','slug',59,'es','sai-esta-salvando-huerfanos-en-venezuela','2022-08-05 20:17:04','2022-10-24 22:23:33'),(454,'blog_posts','meta_description',59,'es','SAI está salvando huérfanos en Venezuela.','2022-08-05 20:17:04','2022-10-24 22:23:33'),(455,'blog_posts','seo_title',58,'es','Clínica Médica SAI en Venezuela.','2022-08-05 21:03:44','2022-10-24 21:53:32'),(456,'blog_posts','title',61,'es','Ayudemos a los zoológicos de Venezuela!','2022-08-05 21:50:54','2022-10-24 23:27:31'),(457,'blog_posts','seo_title',61,'es','Ayúdemos a los zoológicos de Venezuela!','2022-08-05 21:50:54','2022-10-24 23:27:31'),(458,'blog_posts','body',61,'es','<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em;\">Ayudemos a los zool&oacute;gicos de Venezuela!</h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\">Por Steven Malca - Presidente.</div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAI_Ngo_Zoo_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAI_Ngo_Zoo_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Baby Dante!\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAI_Ngo_Zoo_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Beb&eacute; Dante.</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">La Iniciativa Suramericana (SAI) brinda comida, suplementos and cuidado m&eacute;dico a los zool&oacute;gicos y refugios en Venezuela. Podemos decir orgullosamente que nuestro personal y voluntarios han distribuido comida a m&aacute;s de 60 especies en peligro de extinci&oacute;n que habitan en los zool&oacute;gicos y refugios. El programa de rescate animal de SAI ha distribuido m&aacute;s de 2,735 libras de comida en los &uacute;ltimos 6 meses del a&ntilde;o 2022 entre ellas incluyendo Papaya, banana, sand&iacute;a, girasoles, semillas, huevos, proteinas, pescado, vegetales, y leche.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Nuestro beb&eacute; perezoso, Dante, tiene 7 meses de edad, este peque&ntilde;&iacute;n disfruta su nuevo osito de peluche donado por SAI. Dante y su mam&aacute; fueron rescatados hace algunos meses del traf&iacute;co de animales salvajes. Uno de nuestros principales objetivos es proteger y preservar las especies en peligro de extinci&oacute;n en Venezuela.</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">SAI est&aacute; haciendo una diferencia. Gracias por tu apoyo.</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/9d3408f4478d4c14b86fe9955e763e91_1_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Providing food to Zoo Animals Venezuela\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/9d3408f4478d4c14b86fe9955e763e91_1_Grid7.jpeg\" alt=\"Monkey enjoying sunflower seeds, yum!\" width=\"100%\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/9d3408f4478d4c14b86fe9955e763e91_1_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Mono disfrutando sus semillas.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/c96a7375b7c54b629815997bc5579dec_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Rescued Owl!\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/c96a7375b7c54b629815997bc5579dec_Large.jpg\" alt=\"Rescued Owl!\" width=\"100%\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/c96a7375b7c54b629815997bc5579dec_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Buho rescatado.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAINGO_zoo_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Zoo Animal Venezuela\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAINGO_zoo_Large.JPG\" alt=\"Bird rescued!\" width=\"100%\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/39741/SAINGO_zoo_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Aves rescatadas.</div>','2022-08-05 21:50:54','2022-10-24 23:27:31'),(459,'blog_posts','excerpt',61,'es','Help Zoos in Venezuela!','2022-08-05 21:50:54','2022-08-05 21:50:54'),(460,'blog_posts','slug',61,'es','ayudemos-a-los-zoologicos-de-venezuela','2022-08-05 21:50:54','2022-10-24 23:27:32'),(461,'blog_posts','meta_description',61,'es','Ayúdemos a los zoológicos de Venezuela!','2022-08-05 21:50:54','2022-10-24 23:27:32'),(462,'data_rows','display_name',89,'es','Video for spanish page','2022-10-19 03:54:53','2022-10-19 03:54:53'),(463,'data_rows','display_name',90,'es','Summary Es','2022-10-19 03:55:34','2022-10-19 03:55:34'),(466,'blog_posts','title',60,'es','Santuario A&G de SAI actualización.﻿','2022-10-24 22:54:23','2022-10-24 22:54:23'),(467,'blog_posts','seo_title',60,'es','Santuario A&G de SAI actualización.﻿','2022-10-24 22:54:23','2022-10-24 22:54:23'),(468,'blog_posts','body',60,'es','<div class=\"progressReportHeader\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">\n<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=196091\">Santuario A&amp;G de SAI actualizaci&oacute;n.</a></h4>\n<div class=\"byline\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; color: #666666;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=196091\">Por Steven Malca - Presidente.</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary.12_jpg_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Dog rescue Venezuela\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/SAI_AG_Sanctuary.12_jpg_Large.jpg\" alt=\"New arrivals at SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary!\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary.12_jpg_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Reci&eacute;n llegados al santuario A&amp;G de SAI</div>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Estamos orgullosos de anunciar que el santuario A&amp;G de SAI est&aacute; cuidando alrededor de 90-100 perros. Algunos de nuestros perros han sido adoptados por amorosas familias. Y una vez que la fase 2 del santuario est&eacute; completa, el santuario A&amp;G de SAI ser&aacute; capaz de cuidar a m&aacute;s de 170 perros.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">En los &uacute;ltimos 6 meses hemos distribuido un total de 17,710 libras de comida de perro a nuestro santuario y otros 12 refugios de perros. 50.9% de la comida fue destinada a alimentar a los perros de nuestro santuario y el 49,1% restante fue entregada a nuestros refugios asociados.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Podemos anunciar que el programa de rescate animal de SAI est&aacute; ayudando a m&aacute;s de 400 perros brind&aacute;ndoles comida, servicio m&eacute;dico veterinario, medicinas y vacunas a cada perro que llega a nuestro santuario. Adem&aacute;s hemos incrementado la ayuda que brindamos a los refugios asociados con m&aacute;s personal y servicios veterinarios.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span class=\"s1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">El santuario A&amp;G de SAI da la bienvenida a nuestro nuevo veterinario. Con m&aacute;s de 20 a&ntilde;os de experiencia, &eacute;l se ha especializado en entrenamiento de conducta y comportamiento de perros. Es un experto en entrenamiento de socializaci&oacute;n para perros y est&aacute; comparti&eacute;ndonos sus conocimientos para mejorar el servicio que nuestro personal brinda a los perros.</span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; letter-spacing: 0.16px; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Hemos agregado acondicionado y aislamiento t&eacute;rmico en nuestro cuarto de cirug&iacute;a para poseer un ambiente &oacute;ptimo para los perros que entran en cirug&iacute;a. El aire acondicionado y el aislamiento reducen la posibilidad de infecciones del exterior.</span></p>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary21.12_jpg_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Save a dogs life.\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/SAI_AG_Sanctuary21.12_jpg_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"Rescued dog receiving medical care!\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary21.12_jpg_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Perro rescatado recibiendo servicio m&eacute;dico.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG20220608WA0133_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/August2022/IMG20220608WA0133_Large.jpeg\" alt=\"New phase of SAI-A&amp;G sanctuary under construction!\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG20220608WA0133_Large.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">La nueva del santuario A&amp;G de SAI en construcci&oacute;n.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary3221JPG_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Help pets Venezuela\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary3221JPG_Large.JPG\" alt=\"SAI-A&amp;G Dog Food Delivery!\" width=\"100%\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary3221JPG_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Entrega de comida de perro de parte de SAI-A&amp;G.</div>\n<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary322122_Large.JPG\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary322122_Large.JPG\" alt=\"We have nurtured this cutie back to health!\" data-src=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/SAI_AG_Sanctuary322122_Large.JPG\" /></a></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Hemos devuelto la sonrisa a este perrito que lleg&oacute; desnutrido.</div>','2022-10-24 22:54:23','2022-10-24 22:54:23'),(469,'blog_posts','excerpt',60,'es','Rescuing dogs Venezuela.','2022-10-24 22:54:23','2022-10-24 22:54:23'),(470,'blog_posts','slug',60,'es','santuario-aandg-de-sai-actualizacion','2022-10-24 22:54:23','2022-10-24 22:54:23'),(471,'blog_posts','meta_description',60,'es','Santuario A&G de SAI actualización.﻿','2022-10-24 22:54:23','2022-10-24 22:54:23'),(472,'pages','body',21,'es','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe style=\"max-width: 500px; min-width: 250px; max-height: none!important;\" src=\"https://donorbox.org/embed/general-109\" name=\"donorbox\" width=\"100%\" height=\"900px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" seamless=\"seamless\"></iframe></p>','2022-12-02 21:51:22','2023-02-14 05:04:44'),(479,'blog_posts','title',63,'es','SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.','2023-01-23 22:49:25','2023-01-23 22:49:25'),(480,'blog_posts','seo_title',63,'es','SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.','2023-01-23 22:49:25','2023-01-23 22:49:25'),(481,'blog_posts','body',63,'es','<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #3e4b59; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 19.6px; letter-spacing: 0.49px;\">SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado m&eacute;dico a orfanatos de Venezuela.</span></span></h4>\n<p><strong><img title=\"SAI Provides Food To Orphans\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_20221122_124308_116 (1)4.jpg\" alt=\"SAI Provides Food To Orphans\" /></strong></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI entrega comida a orfanatos.</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">South America Initiative continua brindando ayuda m&eacute;dica y comida a orfanatos en Venezuela. Desde Julio hasta Octubre de 2022, SAI ha distribuido m&aacute;s de 15,400 platos de comida a 337 huerfanos en 5 orfanatos afiliados a nuestro programa.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Entre los nutritivos alimentos que proveemos se encuentra: arroz, caraotas, apio, cebolla, cilantro, pollo, sardinas, papas, pasta, t&oacute;mates, harina de maiz, zanahorias, harina de trigo, y frutas como; lechoza, bananas, fresas, sandias, pi&ntilde;as, etc.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Muchos huerfanos son afectados por las inadeacuadas condiciones de los hospitales p&uacute;blicos y la mala alimentaci&oacute;n, nuestra prioridad en SAI es brindar cuidado m&eacute;dico para todos los huerfanos. Nuestra meta es asegurar que cada uno de estos ni&ntilde;os est&eacute;n sanos y felices.</p>\n<p><img title=\"Orphan boy receiving check up by doctor!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_32761.JPG\" alt=\"Orphan boy receiving check up by doctor!\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Huerfanos recibiendo un examen por el doctor.</div>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img title=\"SAI doctor checking vitals for a small orphan boy.\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_32701.JPG\" alt=\"SAI doctor checking vitals for a small orphan boy.\" /></div>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Doctor de SAI haciendo examinaci&oacute;n a huerfano.</div>\n<p><img title=\"Nutritious food for the orphans!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG-20221102-WA00141.jpg\" alt=\"Nutritious food for the orphans!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Comida nutritiva para los huerfanos.</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2023-01-23 22:49:25','2023-01-23 22:49:25'),(482,'blog_posts','excerpt',63,'es','SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.','2023-01-23 22:49:25','2023-01-23 22:49:25'),(483,'blog_posts','slug',63,'es','sai-entrega-comida-y-provee-cuidado-medico-a-orfanatos-de-venezuela','2023-01-23 22:49:25','2023-01-23 22:49:25'),(484,'blog_posts','meta_description',63,'es','SAI entrega comida y provee cuidado médico a orfanatos de Venezuela.','2023-01-23 22:49:25','2023-01-23 22:49:25'),(485,'blog_posts','title',66,'es','Actualización del santuario de perros de SAI-A&G','2023-01-24 18:33:11','2023-01-24 19:16:38'),(486,'blog_posts','seo_title',66,'es','Actualización del santuario de perros de SAI-A&G','2023-01-24 18:33:11','2023-01-24 19:16:38'),(487,'blog_posts','body',66,'es','<h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 15px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Aleo, Georgia, serif; color: #3e4b59; line-height: 1.15; font-size: 1.4em; letter-spacing: 0.025em; text-align: center;\"><a class=\"col_defaultText\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #32404e; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/projects/venezuela-helping-abandoned-pets/reports/?subid=205658\">Actualizaci&oacute;n del santuario de perros de SAI-A&amp;G</a></h4>\n<p><img title=\"Sabrina is at happy at her new home!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_3565.JPG\" alt=\"Sabrina is at happy at her new home!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Sabrina est&aacute; feliz en su nuevo hogar.</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Programa de rescate animal de SAI-A&amp;G Q3</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">En el Q3 (Junio, Julio, Septiembre, Octubre) El programa de rescate animal de SAI entreg&oacute; 13,200 libras de comida de perro (240 sacos), 8,800 libras (160 sacos) fueron al santuario de SAI-A&amp;G y 4,400 libras (80 sacos) fueron distribuidos entre los 18 refugios parte de nuestro programa.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">El santuario de SAI-A&amp;G y los refugios asociados est&aacute;n salvados perros desnutridos, enfermos y abandonados, rescatandolos de las calles de Venezuela. Los perros rescatados tienen parasitos y est&aacute;n desnutridos adem&aacute;s de otros problemas medicos. SAI est&aacute; cuidando a m&aacute;s de 80 perros en nuestro santuario, dandoles comida, agua potable, vacunas, cuidado veterinario, y mucho amor. Adem&aacute;s SAI-A&amp;G provee comida y cuidado veterinario a los 306 perros en nuestros refugios asociados.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Gracias por tus donaciones, estamos salvando la vida de muchos perros juntos.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><img title=\"Vaccine Time!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_3524.JPG\" alt=\"Vaccine Time!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Hora de vacunas.</div>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img title=\"Relaxing while waiting to be groomed!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_3530.JPG\" alt=\"Relaxing while waiting to be groom