family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Los pacientes quieren agradecer a la cl&iacute;nica SAI.</div>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 27.0pt; tab-stops: 45.8pt 91.6pt 137.4pt 183.2pt 229.0pt 274.8pt 320.6pt 366.4pt 412.2pt 458.0pt 503.8pt 549.6pt 595.4pt 641.2pt 687.0pt 732.8pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">SAI provee cuidado m&eacute;dico de alta calidad sin costo a ni&ntilde;os, embarazadas, ancianos y huerfanos. SAI entrega medicinas y cuidado de la salud que son inaccesibles para muchos Venezolanos. Nuestro equipo m&eacute;dico provee cuidado especializado y de calidad a los pacientes.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">En los &uacute;ltimos tres meses, SAI ha brindado los siguientes servicios: examenes medicos, ginecolog&iacute;a, obstetra, ecograf&iacute;as, pediatr&iacute;a para reci&eacute;n nacidos, consulta de nutrici&oacute;n, consultas mensuales para embarazadas, medicinas, vitaminas y suplementes nutricionales sin costo alguna a m&aacute;s de 648 pacientes, entre ellos ancianos, embarazadas, ni&ntilde;os, reci&eacute;n nacidos y huerfanos parte del programa m&eacute;dico de SAI.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">En SAI trabajamos todos los d&iacute;as para salvar vidas y crear un futuro brillante.S&eacute; parte del cambio, &uacute;nete y conviertete en donante mesual. Los huerfanos de Venezuela, embarazadas, ni&ntilde;os y ancianos te necesitan. Ay&uacute;danos a hacer la diferencia.</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><img title=\"Waiting to receive medical care by SAI doctors!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/IMG_13151.JPG\" alt=\"Waiting to receive medical care by SAI doctors!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.16px; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Esperando para ver el doctor.</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em; color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\"><img title=\"SAI doctor provides medical care to infant!\" src=\"https://sai.ngo/public/storage/blog_posts/January2023/SAI_doctor_provides_medical_care_to_infant_Large.jpg\" alt=\"SAI doctor provides medical care to infant!\" /></p>\n<div class=\"caption\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0.25em 0px 0.75em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888; font-family: