rtical-align: baseline; font-size: 0.85em; text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #888888;\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Santuario SAI-A&amp;G 2023 T2 Venezuela - Salvando Perros</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Por Jean Carlos - L&iacute;der de Proyecto</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&iexcl;Bienvenido Dr. Tariba!</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&iexcl;Bienvenido Dr. Tariba!</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">En el segundo trimestre (abril, mayo, junio), el programa de rescate animal de SAI distribuy&oacute; 3,575 libras (65 bolsas) de comida para perros en el Santuario SAI-A&amp;G. Adicionalmente, se repartieron 3,795 libras (69 bolsas) de alimento entre los 18 refugios asociados que reciben el apoyo de SAI-A&amp;G. &iexcl;Total: 7,370 libras de comida para perros! (134 bolsas).</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&iexcl;Estamos emocionados de contar con el Dr. Tariba, nuestro nuevo veterinario, en SAI! Su amplia experiencia en medicina veterinaria ser&aacute; un gran activo para nuestra organizaci&oacute;n. Ha implementado enfoques innovadores que ayudan a mantener el bienestar de nuestros animales, al tiempo que hacen que las operaciones sean m&aacute;s eficientes.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Adem&aacute;s, recientemente instalamos un cenador cubierto en nuestro patio delantero, proporcionando a nuestras queridas mascotas un espacio resguardado para relajarse y mantenerse secos durante los d&iacute;as de lluvia. Para mayor comodidad, colocamos bancos para perros.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.25em;\"><span style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: Open Sans, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.16px;\">Agradecemos su continuo apoyo, convi&eacute;rtase en un donante mensual y trabajemos juntos hacia un futuro m&aacute;s brillante para todos los perros en Venezuela.</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"color: #32404e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.25em; letter-spacing: 0.16px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1.5; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: #457389; text-decoration-line: none; font-weight: bold;\" href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/pfil/34341/IMG_20230719_110647_691_Large.jpg\"><img class=\" lazyloaded\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; margin: 0.5em auto; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: block; clear: both; max-width: 100%;\" title=\"Chilling out on their new benches\" sr